Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What do you want, Rocco?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想要什么 洛可？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.56,0:03:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What we all want.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人们希望的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To not die young, poor or alone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是不想死得早 死得穷 死得孤独{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manny...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}曼尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.77,0:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}These guys, they...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那些家伙…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't give them what they're after,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我不交出他们想要的东西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}they'll kill me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们会杀了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.37,0:03:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hold it, Rocco.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别动 洛可{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We don't fight these guys.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我们不跟那些家伙作对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sure, maybe you get that...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许你能…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Shit. God damn it. - Cut!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 烦 讨厌 - 卡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.71,0:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sorry, everyone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 各位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're going again, Eddie. I don't know what happened.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们再来一次 艾迪 我不知道发生了什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sorry, Sam.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不起 山姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Of course, the one day the author is among us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}偏偏在编剧来的时候出糗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.72,0:03:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Among us. Sure as hell ain't one of us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}虽然他来了 但我们跟他不是一伙的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What's my brilliant line, Trumbo?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的精彩台词是什么 特朗勃？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh! I've got it right here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我正好拿在手上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"sure, maybe you get that long, happy life we all want."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"或许你能如愿活得长长久久"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, what do you got me fighting for then?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你要我对抗什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, peace on Earth. Good will toward men.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大家和平共处 友善待人嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you can't do that. This is America.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没这回事 这里可是美国{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right. How about sex and money?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 那性爱和金钱呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There you go. Two things we all love.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这才像话 二件大家最爱的事物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One of your little sermons on citizenship.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每个美国公民的小小信仰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right, going again.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 重拍一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mayer lined up the A Team.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}米高梅找来了黄金阵容{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sam Wood to shoot, Dalton Trumbo for rewrites.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}山姆·伍德 导演 达尔顿·特朗勃 重写剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.59,0:04:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I had no crew, I couldn't work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}罢工使一切停摆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, good, fingers crossed\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}老天有眼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You wouldn't work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}根本不该让你工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.06,0:04:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}God forbid you cross a picket line for set builders.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你跨越警戒线去布景工人罢工阵营{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What the hell do set builders have to do with writing?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们到底关剧本什么事？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What writers write, builders build.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本中的场景由他们搭建{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What they build, you shoot.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而他们搭的场景由你拍摄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, you make all the money you possibly can.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你靠拍片赚进大把银子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So do I. Why shouldn't they? And why can't we help them?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何他们不能？为何我们不能帮他们？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Listen to you, the swimming pool Soviet.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你家有游泳池 还好意思谈共产主义{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, for God's sakes, you won!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 你赢了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.29,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sam, the strike is over.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}山姆 罢工结束了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you just might try being a gracious winner!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只是想当一个仁慈的胜利者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.71,0:04:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, it's never over with you people!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们这些人真是没完没了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:04:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Strike after strike after strike!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}罢工接二连三{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:04:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"You people"?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"你们这些人"？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.42,0:05:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whatever it takes to seek justice!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们不顾一切只为追求正义{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.55,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hey, you know what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 你都知道什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We've all... Laugh it up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都 一笑而过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Why don't we all take six months off? - Oh, come on, Sam!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们为何不休息他六个月？- 别 山姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I'm gonna go on strike... - Good for you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 那我也要来罢工 - 恭喜你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}against people who go on strike.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抗议那些罢工的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sam, Sam...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}山姆 山姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I won't cross your picket line either.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这次我绝不会越线过去你的阵营{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, give me that, Trumbo! You're just...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我受够了 特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know what? You know what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've spent a hell of a long time... What?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我已经浪费够多时间…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.90,0:05:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're not helping... Eddie...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这不是在帮忙 艾迪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sam, Sam. We gotta talk about those scenes tomorrow.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}山姆 我们得讨论明天要拍的戏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Disaster. Who the hell wrote that crap?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是一场灾难 是谁写的烂戏？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But, uh, first...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不过 首先{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}May I have this dance?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以请你跳一支舞吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie... You're spilling my drink.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪 你把我的酒弄洒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Having fun?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好玩吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eternally.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}永远都这么好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Miss Hopper.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}霍珀小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.29,0:05:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dateline, Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎收看《好莱坞日讯》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The offices of top columnist Hedda Hopper.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}顶尖专栏作家赫达霍珀的办公室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.63,0:05:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Greetings from our film capital,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我从电影之都向大家捎来祝福{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}where all is sun and fun.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里阳光普照 充满乐趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.10,0:05:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Or is it? You see the famous faces here?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？众多名人聚集于此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.14,0:05:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Danny Kaye, Humphrey Bogart,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}丹尼凯 亨佛莱鲍嘉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.94,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}his dishy bride Lauren Bacall.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及他美丽的新娘 洛琳·白考儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All of whom have declared solidarity with film crews\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们都宣称与罢工的剧组人员站在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}picketing for higher wages\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要求提高工资{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in walkouts that quickly turned violent.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}联合罢工迅速转为暴力抗争{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because these strikes were, in fact,\Nthe work of dangerous radicals.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}实则由危险的激进份子策动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Here, we see actor Edward G. Robinson,\Nstar of Double Indemnity.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是《双重保险》中的艾迪华·罗宾森{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And this is writer Dalton Trumbo,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}who is, like many of those strikers and their supporters,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和很多参加并支持罢工的人一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.88,0:06:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a registered communist.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他也是共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who exactly is behind these walkouts?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}联合罢工的幕后黑手是谁？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.63,0:06:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You actually create something...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们创造了电影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.64,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, is that fair?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样公平吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No! No!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不公平 不公平{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Our elected leaders will find out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们的民选众议员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Congressman J. Parnell Thomas\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}约翰·帕奈尔·汤马斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and his House Un-American Activities Committee.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将率领非美活动调查委员会找出答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Communism is not some faraway threat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}共产主义不是远在天边的威胁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's most dangerous agents are here,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最危险的共产分子就在美国{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}controlling the airwaves and movie screens.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}掌握了广播与银幕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.15,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Taking over its employees and their unions.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}控制了旗下的员工与工会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They need to be identified as the enemies they are.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们必须认清 他们就是敌人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.04,0:06:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}NARRATOR: Communists, their goal:\Nworld domination.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}共产分子的目标是统治世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:07:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The frontline of a new kind of war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们发起新型战争{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A cold war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冷战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.59,0:07:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A conspiracy to corrupt democratic values\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}企图败坏民主价值{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and bring about the overthrow of this nation.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并推翻这个国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.26,0:07:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mitzi fell asleep.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}梅兹睡着了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.51,0:07:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hey! That you in the news reel?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就是新闻里的那个人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.89,0:07:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, it was.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是我没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.94,0:07:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Traitor.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}叛徒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, my God! Honey.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 亲爱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.52,0:07:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, I'm all right, I'm all right. No harm done.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没事 我没事 这伤不到我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.11,0:07:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you sure? Oh.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.69,0:07:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Come on. Let's go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来吧 我们走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dad?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you a communist?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是共产党员吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.29,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is that against the law?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样犯法吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.54,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It is not.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.71,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The lady with the big hat said you were a dangerous radical.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那个戴宽帽的女士说 你是危险的激进分子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Radical? Maybe.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}激进分子？或许吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.73,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dangerous. Only to men who fling Cokes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有那些泼可乐的人才会觉得我危险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I love our country.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我热爱国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And it's a good government.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们有一个好政府{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But anything good could be better, don't you think?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但还可以好上加好 你不觉得吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is Mom a communist?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妈是共产党员吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.58,0:08:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Am I?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, why don't we give you the official test?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么 我们来做个正规测验吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.46,0:08:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mom makes your favorite lunch.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一天 妈妈做了你最爱的午餐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ham and cheese.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}火腿起司三明治{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ham and cheese.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}火腿起司三明治{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And at school, you see someone with no lunch at all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}到了学校 你发现有人没午餐吃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What do you do?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会怎么办？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Share.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}分享{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.97,0:08:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Share?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}分享？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you don't tell them to just go get a job?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不会叫他们去找工作？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh. You offer them a loan at 6%. Oh, that's very clever.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不会给他们提供利率6%的贷款？这很明智的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.57,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dad.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah, then you just ignore them.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你是不把他们放在眼里？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.95,0:08:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, well.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You little commie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就是个小共产分子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trumbo, as usual, you only make sense to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃 你讲的话总是只有自己听得懂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, let them call you a communist, me a Democrat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是共产党员 我是民主党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.29,0:09:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're both legitimate parties.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这二个都是合法政党{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yours is just meaner and duller, but there's nothing illegal about any of it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们虽然又贱又烂 但并不违法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.63,0:09:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Yet... - Hunter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你等着瞧 - 汉特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.51,0:09:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Tell your friend to dial down the paranoia and have a drink.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}叫你朋友别再偏执 好好喝酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't think he's being paranoid enough.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我还觉得他不够偏执呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.80,0:09:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not you too.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不会也这样吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.60,0:09:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're out of ice.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的冰块没了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, I have taken the liberty of drawing up a pamphlet.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我自作主张做了一本小册子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The subject: Congress unaware of a little thing\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}主题是 国会还没注意到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.36,0:09:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}called the First Amendment.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有个东西叫宪法第一修正案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're aware of it. They just don't give a shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们当然知道 只是不放在眼里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All they care about is this nice new war of theirs.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们只在乎这场美妙的新战争{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.45,0:09:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}These guys love war and this is a great one,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们热爱战争 这场战争正合他们的意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}'cause it's vague and it's scary and it's expensive.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为既含糊不清 又恐怖而昂贵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Anybody for it is a hero\Nand anybody against it is a traitor.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赞成的就是英雄 反对的就是叛徒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.67,0:09:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}IAN: Exactly, thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}正是如此 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.83,0:09:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Arlen, not near the paintings.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦 别在画旁吸烟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.50,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And if you think this is about the movies, you're an idiot.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别天真地以为他们拍完宣传影片就算了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which is why\NI'm going to have a little chat with the other side.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我决定深入敌方阵营{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.34,0:10:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You don't mean the Alliance, do you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不会是指守护美国理想电影联盟吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I do.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}正是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you out of your mind?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你疯了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.97,0:10:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie, they're all actors and writers and directors,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪 他们是演员 作家和导演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}just like us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就像我们一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're Nazis. They're just too cheap to buy the uniforms.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们是纳粹 只是太过小气不愿买制服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.65,0:10:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They invited Congress out here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们把国会议员都请来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.19,0:10:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And are they all Sam Woods and Hedda Hoppers?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们不就是山姆·伍德和赫达·霍珀吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.36,0:10:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please, let's not demonize people we don't really know.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不要妖魔化我们不了解的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I say we go for it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我赞成{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you know who you're gonna be talking to there, don't you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道 他们请到谁来演讲吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.04,0:10:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ladies and gentlemen, Mr. John Wayne.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各位女士先生 欢迎约翰·韦恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wanna say one thing about a place I love.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想谈谈一个我热爱的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, not Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 不是好莱坞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I like Hollywood, but I love America.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜欢好莱坞 但我更热爱美国{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.73,0:10:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}WAYNE: And when we talk about America,\NI'm talking about freedom.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国代表的就是自由{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.19,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The kind of freedom we just fought a world war to save.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不惜加入世界大战也要捍卫到底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You want to be a communist? Go be a communist.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想加入共产党？那就去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But some friends of mine in Washington\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我在华府的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.74,0:11:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}think you got some questions to answer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}认为你们必须回答几个问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never knew he was this good.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我真不晓得 他这么会说话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}WAYNE: You still want to be a commie...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你们还想加入共产党…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- 'Cause he's not acting. That's him. - go be one in Russia.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 因为他不是在表演 这才是他 - 去莫斯科吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.75,0:11:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But off you go and enjoy the Bolshoi Ballet.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去加入莫斯科大剧院芭蕾舞剧团吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.59,0:11:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Excuse me, sir, would you like to read about the First Amendment?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}先生 想了解宪法第一修正案吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Sir, a little education. - You know your rights?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 学习一点新知 - 你知道自己的权利吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Pamphlet on the First Amendment.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}介绍宪法第一修正案的小册子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- A little light reading. - Travels well.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 只是份轻松读物 - 旅途愉快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, thank you, Sam.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 山姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do svidanya.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}再见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It costs money to print those.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}印小册子是要钱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.40,0:11:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How'd you like to learn\Nabout the First Amendment?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想了解宪法第一修正案吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is a nightmare.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这简直是场恶梦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dalton.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达顿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Hedda. Good evening to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 晚安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie, darling!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的艾迪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.95,0:11:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}New hat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}新帽子？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.66,0:11:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah, daily, darling, daily.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每天都要换一顶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Been to the movies lately, Dalton?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你最近有去看电影吗 达顿？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.63,0:11:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Duke. Now, wasn't he magnificent?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杜克 你们说他是不是棒极了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.96,0:11:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just saying what needs saying. Hi, Eddie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只是说出该说的话 你好 艾迪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Duke.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 杜克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I hear you and your pals got a pamphlet.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听说你和朋友们印了本小册子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.59,0:12:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Any takers? - Not yet.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 有人拿吗？- 还没{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh, would you like one, sir? We're communists.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想拿一本吗？我们是共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's a writer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是剧作家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You won't get any takers. Not here, anyway.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里没有人会拿你们的册子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.48,0:12:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, why is that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.94,0:12:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All it says is that Congress has no right to investigate\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上面只说国会没有权力调查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}how we vote or where we pray,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们给谁投票 去哪里祷告{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}what we think, say or how we make movies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及调查我们的思想言行和电影制作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hello, I'm Dalton Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 我叫达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Congress has the right to go after anything they think is a threat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要国会认定是威胁 就有权力查到底{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, that's where we disagree and that's the point.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们反对这样 重点是…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We both have the right to be wrong.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都应该有犯错的权利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You wanna talk about rights, first tell me whose side you're on.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想谈权利 先告诉我你站在哪一边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Russia's no friend, not anymore.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}俄国已经没有朋友了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.84,0:12:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You'd better wake up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们赶快清醒吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}'Cause it's a new day. A new day!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为新时代已经到来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.06,0:12:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.52,0:12:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And maybe it's not for your kind.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许这时代不适合你这种人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My kind? What kind is that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我这种人？哪一种？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.69,0:13:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The kind that has no idea why we just won a war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不明白我们如何打赢大战的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's curious, that's the second time you mentioned that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真有趣 这是你第二次提及战事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}See, I was a war correspondent in Okinawa.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我以前在冲绳当战地记者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda's son was stationed in the Philippines.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达的儿子被派驻在菲律宾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie was in Europe with the Office of War Information.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪在欧洲的战争情报局工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Where did you serve again?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你当时在哪里服役呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You trying to say something?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, Duke, he wasn't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没什么 杜克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If you're going to talk about World War II as if you personally won it,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你在二战中也有战功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}let's be clear where you were stationed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就请说清楚你被派驻何处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}On a film set, shooting blanks, wearing makeup.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在片场 化着妆 射空包弹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And if you're going to hit me, I would like to take off my glasses.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你要揍我 我想先拿下眼镜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Duke, come on. Let's get out of here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杜克 我们走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.69,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, Dalton. My next column just wrote itself.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 达顿 我的下个专栏有东西写了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.62,0:13:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a good thing you didn't want to demonize anybody\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}幸好你不想妖魔化任何人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.41,0:13:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or else that could have been awkward.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}否则事情就尴尬了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Manny wouldn't say "amorous."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}曼尼不会说"多情"这个字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hang on one second.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.75,0:13:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Paul, two packs, please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保罗 请给我二包烟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.63,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Here you are. - Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 给你 - 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.09,0:14:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Here you go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}钱给你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Good God, she's everywhere.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 她真是无所不在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.72,0:14:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your next deal's gonna make you the highest-paid writer in Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这份合约将让你成为好莱坞薪酬最高的编剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.27,0:14:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which will make you the highest-paid writer in the world.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也就是全世界收入最高的剧作家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You earned it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是你应得的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.77,0:14:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You don't just write happy endings, you actually believe them.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你深信自己写出的快乐结局{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's what people pay to see.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以观众才会买单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's why you belong here at MGM. Right, L.B.?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}米高梅也才会雇用你 是吧 路易？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I hate to make the wooing too easy for you, but where do I sign?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想让你们太容易得逞 那我在哪儿签名？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just one thing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有一个条件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If you're gonna work for me,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如想替我工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I never, ever want to see anything like this again.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就不要再让我看到这种东西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You won't. I promise.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不会的 我保证{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Good.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just stop reading Hedda Hopper.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要你不再读赫达霍珀的专栏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, what did L.B. say then?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}路易跟你说了什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus, don't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别再提了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.44,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I haven't eaten since. My job's not hard enough?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直食不下咽 我的工作还不够辛苦吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your job is not hard at all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一点也不累{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.66,0:15:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You think getting Mayer to sign you after those headlines was easy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你觉得在爆出新闻后 说服梅尔签下你很容易么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.66,0:15:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You have a record-breaking three-year contract to make shit up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}公司提供破纪录的三年合约 供你在纸上胡说八道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're welcome.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用谢我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, honey, not now.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的 现在不是时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.88,0:15:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please, Mom?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 妈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She really can.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她真的可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.72,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Ask her! - Can what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 请她表演 - 可以怎样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cleo, is this true?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}克莉欧 是真的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Watch this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们瞧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.10,0:15:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Trumbo... - Come on.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 特朗勃… - 来啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Of course, you realize this means war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这是在向我挑战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Behold!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大家注意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I had a very unusual mother.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我有个非凡的母亲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Translation: stage mother.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也就是 星妈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.36,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The misspent youth of a child acrobat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杂技演员的悲惨童年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.57,0:15:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My God, how long were you in show business?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 你参加了多久的演出？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.91,0:15:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Till I was 15, but it was more show forced-labor.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}直到我15岁 基本上算是强迫劳动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Bravo! - Brilliant!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 厉害 - 真精彩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Dalton Trumbo?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达尔顿·特朗勃先生？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll see you in Washington.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们华盛顿见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Enjoy your picnic.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}祝你们野餐愉快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's go, boys.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.74,0:16:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, Mr. Stripling, sir.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}遵命 史崔普林先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.45,0:16:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nineteen subpoenas have been issued to those we believe\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们发出了19张传票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}have knowledge of the ongoing communist threat in Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}传唤知悉好莱坞内共党阴谋的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.12,0:16:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What kind of threat is that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么阴谋？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A conspiracy to corrupt democratic values\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}企图败坏民主价值{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and bring about the overthrow of this nation.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并推翻这个国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Using movies?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}利用电影？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Any movie in particular or...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道是哪部吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Movies are the most powerful influence ever created.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}电影是人类史上最具影响力的工具{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And they are infested with hidden traitors.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而隐身幕后的叛徒已染指电影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.27,0:17:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The House Un-American Activities Committee has been formed to investigate\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}众议院非美活动调查委员会成立{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}alleged communists working in Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}调查好莱坞中可疑的共党分子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The newsreel cameras and an army of newspapermen are on hand.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}摄影机和一队记者记录了现场的情景{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Reagan, has it been reported to you\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}里根先生你是否知悉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There has been a small group more or less following the tactics\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一小群人 或多或少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.24,0:17:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that we, uh, associate with the Communist Party.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}和共产党有些接触{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And would you refer to them as a disrupting influence?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你认为他们是破坏分子吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.21,0:17:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I would say that, at times, they have attempted to be a disruptive influence.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们有时试图成为破坏分子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do you believe that the motion picture industry\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你认为电影界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.09,0:17:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is doing everything it can to rid itself\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已尽力不成为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}of subversive un-American influences?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}颠覆美国的势力吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. Communists are everywhere.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 共产党员无所不在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.01,0:17:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They report directly to Moscow.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们直接向莫斯科汇报{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}On numerous occasions, communist agitators have tried hard\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}煽动共产主义的人在许多场合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to steer us into the red river.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}试图让我们沦陷于赤色思潮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.69,0:17:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We had a little too much weight for that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我们的立场坚定不移{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Will you name a few of these agitators?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你能指出几位煽动分子吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.16,0:18:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, Irving Pichel,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欧文·皮切尔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.37,0:18:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Edward Dmytryk, Frank Tuttle.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪华·狄米屈克 法兰克·杜托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I had my way about it,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若由我作主{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}they'd all be sent back to Russia\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就把他们全送回俄国{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.00,0:18:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or some other unpleasant place.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或是其他不毛之地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.25,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We get our chance to testify in three days.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们得在三天内出面作证{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And what we're about to do won't make us too popular.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而这会损害我们的名誉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Okay, so we get slandered and then what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就算我们被人诋毁 那又如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.68,0:18:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You answer every question they ask in your own way.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就用你的方式回答他们每一个问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.27,0:18:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, don't tell them shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就别跟他们抬杠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.85,0:18:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beautifully put.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}说得好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you know what they call that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道他们给我们起的罪名吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.02,0:18:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In all likelihood, we'll be cited for contempt of Congress.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们十之八九会被指为藐视国会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.53,0:18:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There will be a trial.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们会被审判{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.61,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What am I missing here?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没听错吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All I'm hearing is jail.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只听到了坐牢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not necessarily.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不见得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.87,0:18:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In a lower court, yes, we'll most likely lose.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在低等法庭我们应该会输{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- But on appeal... - It'll work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 但上诉之后 - 一定能成功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.21,0:18:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Supreme Court is a five-to-four liberal majority.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最高法院大法官九人中有五人是自由派{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They think this committee is unconstitutional.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们认为委员会违宪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.29,0:18:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They want it killed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不除不快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sounds great.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听起来不错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.38,0:18:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我退出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niki.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮琪再见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look, I can't afford this stuff you guys are talking about.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们的计划我承担不起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.94,0:19:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Supreme Court and legal fees...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}包括上诉最高法院以及法律费用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.23,0:19:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, Dorothy's not gonna...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}桃乐丝一定不会同意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.40,0:19:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, things already aren't great, but you know...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的情况已不乐观{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.78,0:19:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I dump all my savings into that, she's gone with the kids.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若再赌上所有积蓄 她会带孩子走人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll cover you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我帮你出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.99,0:19:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Expenses, travel, legal fees, everything.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开销 旅费 诉讼费全由我付{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.41,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You don't even like me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是你明明不喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I like you fine. You don't like me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜欢你 是你不喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.63,0:19:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, you know what it is? I don't trust you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道吗 我不相信你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.93,0:19:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I'd say go on, but I'm afraid you will.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不用我提 你也会继续说下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.43,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look, I know what I am. Okay?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我知道自己有几两重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I want this whole country\Nto be different, top to bottom.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我当然希望举国上下焕然新生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I get what I want, nobody gets their own lake.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若由我作主 没有人家里能有一座湖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, that would be a very dull life, don't you think?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样的人生多无趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.94,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, for you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对你而言是如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not for the guys who built this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但造湖工人不这么认为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.15,0:19:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I'm wrong, tell me, but ever since I've known you,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许是我错了 但从我们认识以来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.61,0:20:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you talk like a radical.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你言论激进{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But you live like a rich guy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}却仍过着富裕生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That is true.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你没搞错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't think you're willing to lose all of this just to do the right thing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不觉得你会为了做正确的事牺牲这一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I despise martyrdom and I won't fight for a lost cause.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我反对殉教 也不打没胜算的仗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.17,0:20:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you're right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm not willing to lose it all. Certainly not them.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不愿失去一切 尤其是孩子们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.51,0:20:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But I am willing to risk it all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我愿意赌一把{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.97,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's where the radical and the rich guy make a perfect combination.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是激进分子和有钱人的综合体{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.97,0:20:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The radical may fight with the purity of Jesus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}激进分子依循耶稣的纯洁教诲奋战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the rich guy wins with the cunning of Satan.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而有钱人则因撒旦的奸巧获胜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.40,0:20:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}够了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.90,0:20:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just please shut up. Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托你闭嘴 好吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll do whatever you want.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要我做什么都可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just please don't say shit like that anymore.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只求你别再跟我说这些鬼话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.42,0:20:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I can't guarantee that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我无法保证{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.21,0:21:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In Washington, 10 of the original 19 subpoenaed\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}传唤的19人中 有10人抵达华盛顿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}began their testimony before the House Un-American Activities Committee.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开始在非美活动调查委员会面前作证{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.68,0:21:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo, raise your right hand.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生 请举起右手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do you solemnly swear the testimony you are about to give\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请宣誓 接下来所说的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is the truth, the whole truth, nothing but the truth so help you God?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}句句属实{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.02,0:21:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I do.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我发誓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sit down, please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请坐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.62,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo, now I shall ask you a series of various questions\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生 接下来我会问你一些问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all of which can be answered with a yes or a no.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只需要回答是或不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.24,0:21:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I shall answer yes or no if I please to answer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想回答是或不是 就会回答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I shall answer in my own words.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会回答自己想说的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.20,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Many questions can be answered yes or no\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不是每个问题都能用或否来回答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.00,0:21:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}only by a moron or a slave.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非对方是白痴或奴隶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's enough!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}够了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.87,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you refusing to answer the question?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你拒绝回答问题吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Chairman, I will refuse to answer none of your questions.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}主席 你的任何问题我都不会拒答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you now or have you ever been\Na member of the Communist Party?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你现在或曾经是否加入过共产党？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.97,0:21:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}May I introduce to evidence...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想提出证物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.97,0:21:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. No! You are out of order!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 违反规则{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- my work, my screenplays... - No, no, no, no, no, no.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 证据就是我写的剧本 - 不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}by which you are making this determination?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你可能依此做出这样的判断{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, the chair will rule.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切由主席裁决{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.39,0:21:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- It's critical to... - No, just a minute.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 但这是关键 - 不行 没有时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.14,0:21:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your screenplays are too long.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的剧本太长了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.73,0:21:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've heard that before.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这句话我以前也听过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you now or have you ever been a member of the Communist Party?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你现在或曾经是否加入过共产党？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.90,0:22:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Am I accused of a crime?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你指控我有罪？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.41,0:22:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're not asking the questions.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你没有回答问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.61,0:22:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If so, I believe I have the right to be confronted\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若是如此 我有权与指控我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.41,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}with any evidence that supports this question.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}证据与证人对质{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you refusing to answer the...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你拒绝回答问题么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I should very much like to see what you have.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想看看你的证据{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.50,0:22:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, you would? You will see very soon!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？我马上会拿给你看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.29,0:22:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Good!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.67,0:22:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The witness is excused.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}证人请离席{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You believe this committee has the right to compel testimony.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你认为委员会有权强迫证言{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.42,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You are dismissed, sir! Witness is dismissed!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你离席{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.43,0:22:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To indict opinion, to criminalize thought...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你指控一个人的思想有罪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.09,0:22:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guard, take him out!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}警卫 带他下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- but that right does not exist, sir! - Order!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 但你没有这样的权利 - 肃静{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.97,0:22:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the moment it does, God help us all!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上帝会在关键时刻帮助我们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.10,0:22:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is typical communist tactic!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这就是典型的共产党策略！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is the beginning of an American concentration camp!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国也开始办集中营了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.44,0:22:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Order!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肃静{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh, state your name, please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请报上姓名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.61,0:22:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Arlen Hird. I'm a screenwriter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦赫德 我是剧作家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.94,0:22:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You understand, sir, that if you don't answer my questions,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你不回答我的问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I can hold you in contempt of Congress?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将因藐视国会而遭羁押{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I didn't refuse yet, did I?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我还没有拒绝回答吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.45,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you now or have you ever been\Na member of the Communist Party?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你现在或曾经是否加入过共产党？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.81,0:22:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I'd like to answer you, Congressman,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很乐意回答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but I need to consult with my physician.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我得先问问我的医生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.12,0:22:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Your physician? - Yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 医生？- 是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.21,0:22:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't understand.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.29,0:23:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To find out if he can surgically remove my conscience.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看他是否能动手术 切除我的良心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is a hostile witness.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们都是敌意证人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.55,0:23:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is typical communist tactics.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这就是典型的共产党策略{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Arlen. Arlen, what is it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦 你怎么了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.98,0:23:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's cancer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得了癌症{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.86,0:23:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How long have you known?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道多久了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Three months. - Months?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 三个月前 - 才几个月？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.83,0:23:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you receiving treatment?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有接受治疗吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh, I don't like the options.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不喜欢那些治疗法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.00,0:23:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's lung cancer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得了肺癌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bad if you operate, bad if you don't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开不开刀都一样糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.67,0:23:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, is there anything I can do for you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能帮上什么忙吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.85,0:23:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No! No, it's cancer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你帮不上忙 我得的是癌症{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.85,0:23:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, but...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是 但是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.93,0:23:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.39,0:24:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You want to do something? Make sure this plan works.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想帮忙 就确保这计划成功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.94,0:24:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm out of options.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我已别无选择{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.79,0:24:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We were so young. We thought we knew everything.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们年轻时 自以为神通广大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.55,0:24:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We did.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们确实是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.13,0:24:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, not me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 我不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.47,0:24:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, I didn't realize how much I loved it all\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}年轻时我还不知道自己多爱演戏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.14,0:24:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}until I reached a certain age, and the roles started drying up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}直到上年纪后戏约越来越少才明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.14,0:24:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I remember thinking, "Now what do you do\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当时我想 我所钟情的事物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"when you love something but it stops loving you back?"\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若不再钟情于我 该怎么办？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You fight.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}挺身而战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.48,0:24:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no, no. You love it more until it surrenders.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 你要更深爱它 直到它向你投降{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.73,0:24:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda, you never left MGM or my heart.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 你一直在米高梅和我心里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.62,0:24:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How's your boy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你儿子最近好吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.12,0:24:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Fine. Fine.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.58,0:24:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Still in the navy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还在海军？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.00,0:25:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, he's First Lieutenant.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 他是上尉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.83,0:25:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You raised a real hero.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你养育了一个真正的英雄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.83,0:25:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which is why I would like to tell him\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以我想告诉他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.50,0:25:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that we are doing as much for this country as he is.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们也跟他一样 努力报效国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.96,0:25:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's complicated.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}事情很复杂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.63,0:25:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trumbo, the others, all have contracts.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃等人手上都有合约{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.84,0:25:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, L.B., you helped build this business as did I.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}路易 你跟我一样白手起家打下江山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.51,0:25:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're not gonna watch these pissants defile it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎能容许这些废物毁了一切？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.98,0:25:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm running a studio here, Hedda.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 我经营电影片厂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.35,0:25:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You think I love every person on my payroll?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以为每个员工我都喜欢吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.94,0:25:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Grow up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该长大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.86,0:25:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Then how about I make it crystal clear to my 35 million readers\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不如我向3500万读者明确指出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.11,0:25:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}exactly who runs Hollywood and won't fire these traitors?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哪些好莱坞大佬不愿开除叛徒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.79,0:25:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How about I name names? Real names.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不如写出这些赤色分子的本名吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.54,0:25:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jacob Warner, Jack Warner, Schmuel Gelbfisz, Sam Goldwyn.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}雅各布·华纳 杰克·华纳 塞缪尔·戈尔德温 山姆·高德温{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.34,0:25:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And of course, yours. Lazar Meir.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然还有你 路易·梅尔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.51,0:25:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You watch what you say to me!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你放尊重点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.05,0:25:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Forty years ago, you were starving in some shtetl.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}40年前你还在犹太家乡挨饿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.97,0:26:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The greatest country on Earth takes you in, gives you wealth, power.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世上最伟大国家接纳你 赐你金钱权势{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.64,0:26:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the second we need you, you do nothing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但当我们需要你时 你却袖手旁观{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.64,0:26:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And that's exactly what my readers expect\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在我读者的心目中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.23,0:26:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}from a business run by kikes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}犹太佬正是如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.82,0:26:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Get out!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}滚出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.15,0:26:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, L.B., I am fond of you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}路易 我很喜欢你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.82,0:26:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Some of my happiest years were spent on this lot.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在这片厂度过许多愉快岁月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.49,0:26:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not in your office, of course.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然不是在你办公室里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.58,0:26:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You were always trying to fuck me on the couch.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你总是想在沙发上要我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.00,0:26:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Me, trying to maintain my virtue... Barely.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只能尽力维护贞操 却仍差点失守{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.67,0:26:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But times change.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但是斗转星移{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.50,0:26:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now I'd happily fuck you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在换我笑着上你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.59,0:26:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All studios unanimously agree to discharge the Hollywood Ten\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有片厂一致同意开除好莱坞十君子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.89,0:26:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}without compensation, effective immediately.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不提供补偿 决议立即生效{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.52,0:26:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No studio will ever employ a member of the Communist Party\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有片厂都不会雇用共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.19,0:26:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or anyone refusing to cooperate\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或任何不愿配合对抗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.40,0:26:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in our struggle with this terrible new menace.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这可怕的新威胁的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.90,0:27:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's been loved by film fans for almost 20 years.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}20年来 他一直是影迷的最爱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.45,0:27:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But have you noticed he hasn't been on-screen much lately?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但你们发现了吗？最近电影里都没有他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bad box office?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}票房不好？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.08,0:27:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. Bad politics.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 是政治立场不对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.92,0:27:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bad news indeed for Mr. Edward G. Robinson.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对艾迪·华罗宾森而言 这真是个坏消息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.04,0:27:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you so much for coming.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢各位出席{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.46,0:27:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Hollywood Ten are going to court for all of us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好莱坞十君子将为所有电影人上法庭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.26,0:27:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It'll be long, expensive,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这将会是场漫长昂贵的诉讼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.30,0:27:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}so please give as much as you can to the defense fund.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请尽量慷慨解囊 捐助辩护基金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you for coming.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感谢各位莅临{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.73,0:27:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Good night, my dear. - Good luck.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 晚安 亲爱的 - 祝你好运{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.73,0:27:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Good night, sir. Thank you. - Bye-bye.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 晚安先生 谢谢 - 再见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.06,0:27:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, this little gathering didn't quite have\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}聚会比不过去年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.78,0:27:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the zip and zing of yesteryear, did it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么有声有色 是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.40,0:27:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Where are all the liberals all of a sudden?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那些自由主义者在哪里？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.57,0:27:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}At their lawyers' or psychiatrists'.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去找律师或精神科医生了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.91,0:27:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hmm, likely both.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}应该两者都有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.83,0:27:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}For the defense fund.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}捐给辩护基金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.12,0:27:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.16,0:27:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Have you been working?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你最近有工作吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.62,0:27:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eh. It's a bit slow.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}生意有点清淡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.13,0:27:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You sold one.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你卖了一幅画{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.92,0:28:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, the van Gogh.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}梵高那幅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Got a good price.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}卖了个好价钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.51,0:28:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.26,0:28:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dear God, look at this. Eddie, I can't let you do...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 你看这数字 艾迪我不能收{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.14,0:28:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll be fine, kid, take it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没事 收下吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.60,0:28:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, it's too much. It's just too much.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 实在太多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.98,0:28:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Take it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}收下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.19,0:28:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie, I...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪 我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.28,0:28:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Everything that you have...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你所做的一切…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.20,0:28:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What he's trying to say is that he loves you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他想说的是 他爱你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.50,0:28:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I love him too, the warty son of a bitch.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也爱他 脸上长疣的混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.88,0:28:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Got a great offer on the Monet if you want to bribe the jury.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要是你想贿赂陪审团 有人给莫奈的画出了高价{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.13,0:28:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In the matter of the United States v. Dalton Trumbo,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国政府控告达尔顿·特朗勃一案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.47,0:28:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}we find the defendant guilty of contempt of Congress.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}陪审团认定被告藐视国会罪名成立{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.98,0:28:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo! Mr. Trumbo!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.23,0:28:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll meet you in the car.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们车上见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.36,0:28:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo, are you in contempt of Congress?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生 你是否藐视国会？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.40,0:29:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I have total contempt of this Congress.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我当然看不起他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.90,0:29:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just thought the jury would see why.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只是我以为陪审团将理解为什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.49,0:29:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Supreme Court will drop kick\Nthis verdict into speeding traffic\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最高法院会迅速驳回陪审团的裁定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.70,0:29:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and end the most shameful chapter\Nin Congressional history.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}终结这出国会史上最羞耻的闹剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.83,0:29:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, that's it, boys. We have nothing else.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}够了 没别的话可说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.87,0:29:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, we're done, we're done.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}采访结束{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.54,0:29:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}KENNY: How are you doing for money?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的经济状况如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.21,0:29:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Broke as a bankrupt's bastard. Why?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}穷到喝西北风了 怎样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.84,0:29:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you owe me $30,000, and this appeal's gonna be twice that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你欠我三万元 上诉费用还要加倍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.84,0:29:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I'd better get to work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我最好赶紧去开工赚钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.38,0:29:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Doing what? You have no talent to do anything else.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}做什么？你没有能力做别的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.85,0:29:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}NARRATOR: Hollywood fights back!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好莱坞大反攻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.02,0:29:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is Gregory Peck.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是葛雷哥莱毕克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.60,0:29:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A state of near hysteria\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国已近乎歇斯底里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.35,0:29:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}over so-called communists in this country\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}指控所谓的共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.60,0:29:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}threatens the freedom of other citizens.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}威胁国民自由{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.07,0:29:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the Un-American Committee bears its tragic fruit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非美活动调查委员会则延续了此悲剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.78,0:29:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is Lucille Ball.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是露西·波儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.74,0:29:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All of us agree that the Constitution of the United States must be defended.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都同意 应该捍卫美国宪法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.37,0:29:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But the way to do this is not by shutting up the man you disagree with.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但使反对者噤声并非正当作为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.04,0:29:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You must fight for his right to speak and be heard.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们必须捍卫对方表达且被聆听的权利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.25,0:30:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All civil liberties go hand in hand.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}各项自由都是牵一发动全身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.96,0:30:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And when one goes, the others are weakened.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有一项沦陷 其他便岌岌可危{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.09,0:30:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just as a collapse of one pillar in a house\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一柱垮塌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.09,0:30:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}would endanger the whole structure.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大厦将倾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.40,0:30:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We'll send you home in a couple of days.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}过几天你就能回家了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.23,0:30:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, it sounds like you're going to live.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听起来你还能活下去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.28,0:30:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, they got me just well enough to go to prison.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们得治好我 才能送我进监牢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.62,0:30:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How do you feel?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你觉得如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.58,0:30:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Breathing with one lung, which is half as good as two.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只能用一边肺呼吸 感觉只吸到一半{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.25,0:30:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look, Arlen, I heard about Dorothy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦 我听说桃乐丝的事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.75,0:30:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, she took off.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错 她离开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.96,0:30:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Her timing was always amazing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她总是很会挑时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.59,0:30:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm sorry.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很遗憾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.14,0:30:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, well, I know. I mean, how could you leave all this?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 她怎么能就这样远走高飞？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.85,0:30:58.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How's it going out there?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}外头状况如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.02,0:31:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Everyone envies you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大家都很嫉妒你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.69,0:31:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, why wouldn't they?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.82,0:31:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I got the best room in the joint.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得到了苦窑里最棒的房间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.95,0:31:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You should know. You paid for it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你一定知道 因为钱是你出的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.87,0:31:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Congratulations, Buddy. - Thank you, fellas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 恭喜你 巴迪 - 谢谢各位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.16,0:31:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who needs the studios? I am strictly independent.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁需要那些片厂？我完全独立自主{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.67,0:31:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Got cans of film, wads of Wall Street dough,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有底片 有华尔街的资金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.54,0:31:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and my favorite boss, me. (ALL LAUGH)\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有最棒的老板 我自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.34,0:31:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cheers. Cheers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}干杯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.72,0:31:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you, you crazy son of a bitch,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这个疯子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.39,0:31:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you're gonna write all of my movies once this Washington crap clears up.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等这鬼官司结束 所有电影都交给你写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.97,0:31:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And how will that happen?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么才能结束呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.73,0:31:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm not political, thank Jesus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感谢老天 我不关心政治{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.98,0:31:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If they called me in, accused me, I'd just say,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果他们传唤我 指控我 我会说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.02,0:31:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"Yup, did it. Sorry, didn't mean it."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 我不是故意的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.82,0:31:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So Congress then asks,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}接着国会问你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.73,0:31:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"Are you now or have you ever been a Democrat?"\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是否曾加入民主党？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.07,0:31:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am and, God, I just feel awful about it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是民主党员 天啊 我觉得糟透了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.08,0:32:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Then they want the names of other Democrats.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后他们会要你供出民主党员名单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bill and Earl, Nate, Tom.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}例如比尔 厄尔 奈特和汤姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.30,0:32:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Then I say, "Go to hell."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会说 去吃屎吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.67,0:32:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Really?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.43,0:32:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How many banks fund enemies of the state?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有哪些银行愿意资助政府的敌人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.68,0:32:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your money's gone unless you give the names\Nof your friends here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非供出朋友的名字 否则拿不到钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.43,0:32:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They'll never work again,\Nbut it's the only way you ever will.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们永远无法工作 但如此你才能存活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.65,0:32:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We all know each other, our families.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们彼此相熟 包括我们的家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.82,0:32:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're friends.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们是朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.16,0:32:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What would you do, Buddy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会怎么做 巴迪？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.83,0:32:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Only you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.79,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Piss on the best day of a guy's life.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}会毁了别人一生最美好的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.04,0:32:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Only you!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.68,0:32:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Christ's sakes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.72,0:33:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}According to the protocol set forth...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"根据协议…"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.73,0:33:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And what does she say?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她会怎么说？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.73,0:33:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What does the princess say?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}公主会说什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.24,0:33:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Shit... Shit!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可恶 烂透了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.88,0:33:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Shouldn't be any likeness...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"应该一点都不像才对"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.38,0:33:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It concerns me a little bit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"这让我有点担心"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.42,0:33:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, good morning, Nikola.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}早安 妮可拉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.09,0:33:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I thought you weren't allowed to write anymore.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我以为你不能写剧本了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.26,0:33:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah. No. No, just not allowed to put my name on it,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 只是剧本上不能有我的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.94,0:33:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or get paid.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或直接付钱给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.77,0:33:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How does that work?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是什么状况？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.23,0:33:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not very well.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}状况不太好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.94,0:33:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's funny. It's breezy and romantic.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这故事很有趣 轻松又浪漫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.28,0:33:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who wrote it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是谁写的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.45,0:34:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You did, old boy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你写的 老弟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.87,0:34:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You stick your name on my labor,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的剧本写上你的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.96,0:34:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}hand it in to your studio and we're in business.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}交给公司就成了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.79,0:34:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look, it is just dumb luck that I wasn't subpoenaed and blacklisted myself.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没被传唤或列入黑名单只是侥幸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.09,0:34:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The hearings are going to start up again soon.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下一波审讯即将展开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.80,0:34:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm going to get called and canned.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也可能会被停工或解雇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.92,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, then quick, lad.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那手脚要更快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's sell this little beauty and split the take, 50-50.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本卖成了 我们五五分帐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.89,0:34:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ridiculous. I'll take 10%.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}荒唐 我收一成就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.64,0:34:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You'll take 20. No, 30! And that's my final offer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你收二成 不 三成 这是我的底线{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.94,0:34:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're the worst businessman ever.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是全世界最烂的生意人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.82,0:34:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I hate the title.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我讨厌这片名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.40,0:34:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Me too.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.90,0:34:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Really? What's wrong with it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哪里不好？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.15,0:34:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- The Princess and the Peasant. - Yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 《公主与乡巴佬》？ - 是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.11,0:34:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}God, please, Trumbo, it sounds like a puppet show.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 听起来像出偶剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.49,0:34:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, then, change it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就改掉吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.74,0:34:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}改了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.75,0:34:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Really? You think this title's better?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的？你觉得这个名字更好？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.08,0:34:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Roman Holiday.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《罗马假日》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.46,0:34:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I like it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我喜欢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.30,0:34:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who invited you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁让你加入的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.67,0:34:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.51,0:34:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She's my favorite Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她是我最喜欢的特朗勃家庭成员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.18,0:35:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm introducing legislation\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要立法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.11,0:35:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}so in the event of a national emergency,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在此国家危急时刻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.10,0:35:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all communists will be sent to internment camps.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有共产党员都会被送进俘虏收容所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.19,0:35:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the president supports this?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}总统支持此案么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.94,0:35:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He better.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他最好能支持{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.27,0:35:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Parnell, I need to speak to you privately about your employees.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帕奈尔 我们得谈谈你的员工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.99,0:35:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Excuse me, gentlemen.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我先失陪了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.20,0:35:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}As I said, Bob, these are legitimate salaried employees from my home state.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些都是我家乡的合法支薪员工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.03,0:35:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What you didn't tell me is that every one of them is a relative.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但你没告诉我 他们都是你的亲戚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.70,0:35:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which is completely legal.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这完全合法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.87,0:35:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Except that none of them pay taxes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是他们都没缴税{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.71,0:35:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Don't say anything else without a lawyer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等你的律师到场后再说吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.22,0:35:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.47,0:35:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mrs. Trumbo! Hi.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃太太 你好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.06,0:35:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jeff.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杰夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.97,0:35:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ma'am, I gotta get paid.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}太太 你该付我工钱了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.73,0:35:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh. I'm so sorry.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.80,0:35:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I got men with families.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的人都要养家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.31,0:35:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My husband hasn't been able to get any work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我丈夫无法工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.53,0:35:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We owe everyone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们四处欠债{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.24,0:35:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Ma'am, please. - I'm so...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 太太 拜托 - 真的很抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.24,0:36:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cleo, we're rich!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}克莉欧 我们有钱了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.74,0:36:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There you are, Jeffrey.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿去吧 杰夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.12,0:36:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You people sure live exciting lives.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们的生活真刺激{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.75,0:36:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I thank you. Appreciate it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你的帮忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.04,0:36:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, Betty!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也谢谢你贝蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.59,0:36:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We did it, Cleo!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们成功了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.38,0:36:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We sold Roman Holiday! Paramount.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}派拉蒙买了《罗马假日》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.22,0:36:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Our beloved Ian is just...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的 伊恩刚刚…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.93,0:36:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why, what's the matter?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.05,0:36:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Judge Rutledge died.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拉特利奇大法官死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.34,0:36:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no, that was Judge Murphy who died last month.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上个月死的是墨菲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.43,0:36:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And Rutledge.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拉特利奇也死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.77,0:36:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Last night.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}昨晚过世{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.57,0:36:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, now...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别担心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.11,0:36:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Everything will be all right. You'll see.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都会没事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.41,0:36:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Without a liberal majority on the court,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}自由派大法官不占多数{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.79,0:36:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}our appeal's gonna be denied.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上诉将被驳回{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.62,0:36:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Meaning we should all be prepared to go to prison.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也就是说 我们都要准备坐牢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.51,0:37:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wouldn't change anything going back. Not one thing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就算从头来过 我也不会改变任何决定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.69,0:37:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's ask each other in a year.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一年后我们再问问彼此吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.12,0:37:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Will you do me a favor?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}帮我个忙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.70,0:37:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hold on to this while I'm gone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不在时帮我保管这个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.62,0:37:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, dear.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 亲爱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.38,0:37:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your mother needs to laugh at least once a day.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每天都要逗妈妈笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.67,0:37:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Deal?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一言为定？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.92,0:37:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Okay.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.22,0:37:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Where's that little pumpkin seed?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的小可爱去哪了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.52,0:37:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- To the Hollywood Ten! - Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 敬好莱坞十君子 - 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.36,0:38:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To the Hollywood Ten!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}敬好莱坞十君子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.03,0:38:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're heroes!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们是英雄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.03,0:38:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}28 cents. Gold lighter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}28美分 金色打火机{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:46.90,0:38:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wallet. Cigarette case.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}皮夹 烟盒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.04,0:38:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Raise your hands.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}举手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.62,0:39:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Open your mouth. Wider.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}张开嘴巴 张大点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.04,0:39:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Turn your head to the right. To the left.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}头转右边 转左边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.46,0:39:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Tilt your head back.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}头往后仰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.43,0:39:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Spread your legs.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}腿张开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.39,0:39:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Grab your sack and skin it back.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拿起阴囊 拉起来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.73,0:39:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Turn around.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.90,0:39:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Spread your cheeks.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拨开屁股{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.94,0:39:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Squat. Cough.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}蹲下 咳嗽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.61,0:39:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Turn around.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}转身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.79,0:39:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Move out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.50,0:39:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Next!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下一位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So the warden says I gotta do right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}典狱长要我好好处置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.80,0:39:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Boy want a better job?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他想要更好的工作？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.64,0:39:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I put him in charge of the whole goddamn supply room.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就派他去管该死的储藏室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.14,0:39:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}'Cause I know something the warden don't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为我知道典狱长不知道的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.98,0:40:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Truck's unloaded. Driver needs a signature.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}货都搬下来了 卡车司机要我们签收{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.33,0:40:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Actually, uh, he needs it right here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其实 他需要签在这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.72,0:40:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, if, uh... If you need any help,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你需要任何协助{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.39,0:40:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I used to run shipping at a... At a bakery.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我以前在烘焙坊做进出货{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.90,0:40:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Heard you's a writer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我听说你是剧作家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.44,0:40:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, that too.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}身兼二职{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.02,0:40:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And a commie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也是共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.82,0:40:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What the fuck is wrong with you people?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们这些人有什么毛病？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.57,0:40:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is a great country.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国是个伟大的国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.99,0:40:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Agreed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我同意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.03,0:40:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You type?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你会打字吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.21,0:41:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Stop.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}停{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.34,0:41:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, now, if only I could read it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但愿我能识字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.68,0:41:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"Protocol as to return of goods.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"退还货品协议"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.73,0:41:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"There shall be triplicate copies of Form 14-A filed\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"应准备一式三份文件"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.40,0:41:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"with Supply, Shipping and Office of the Warden."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"归档于储藏室 运送处与典狱长室"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.61,0:41:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You think you're gonna teach me the alphabet\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以为我会请你教我识字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.78,0:41:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and I'm gonna shake your hand all grateful and say,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然后跟你握手说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.24,0:41:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"Thank you, Mr. Trumbo. You done change my life, sir.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"感谢改变我的一生"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.29,0:41:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"I'll never forget you."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"我不会忘记你"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.42,0:41:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I got 20 years for killing me a white man who tried to rob my bar.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我杀了想抢我酒吧的白人 被判20年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.30,0:41:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did it and I'd do it again.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不介意再干一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.93,0:41:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You look down on me and I will fuck you up like you've never been fucked up\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会搞死瞧不起我的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.39,0:42:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in your whole bullshit Beverly Hills life.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让你享受在比佛利山庄没吃过的苦头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.27,0:42:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now I'm here trying to build my time and make parole.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我现在要努力申请假释{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.73,0:42:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You wanna help make that happen?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要帮我吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.82,0:42:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Welcome to fucking Supply, Comrade.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎来到该死的储藏室 同志{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.33,0:42:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dear Cleo, I don't count the days or hours...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}克莉欧 我不计算过了几天或几小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.13,0:42:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I count the seconds.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而是数秒度日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.30,0:42:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sometimes I think I'll die of boredom. Other times, fear.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有时我以为自己将因厌倦或恐惧而死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.18,0:42:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not of this place.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里并不可怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.93,0:42:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So far, its challenges are all surmountable.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}目前所有挑战我都能克服{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.43,0:42:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Augmented by days of lovely boredom.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不怕与日俱增的无聊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.31,0:42:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So flat and calm in the wake of all that churning ugly luckless battle.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}也不怕在丑恶不幸的打斗后平静醒来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.65,0:42:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, my fear is for what will happen when I get out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 我怕的是出去之后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.45,0:43:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To our family and our country.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不知道家庭和国家会变成什么模样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.83,0:43:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not all the news is worrisome.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并非所有消息都值得忧虑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.83,0:43:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Some reminds me that what the imagination can't conjure\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有些事情超乎想像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.54,0:43:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}reality delivers with a shrug.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}却轻易抖落于现实之中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.21,0:43:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And reality has delivered in all its beatific wonder\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现实开了一个大玩笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.01,0:43:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to the federal penal system, J. Parnell Thomas,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}把约翰·帕奈尔·汤马斯送进监狱里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.85,0:43:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}convicted of tax evasion.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他因逃漏税入狱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.02,0:43:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, look at us. Just a couple of jailbirds.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}瞧瞧我们 二只笼中鸟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.69,0:43:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Except you actually committed a crime.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只不过 你是真的犯了罪才进来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.65,0:43:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yet in all this,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}撇开一切种种{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.66,0:43:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I know I'm the luckiest unlucky man ever to live,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我已是不幸之人中最幸运的了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.20,0:43:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}because you and the children warm, feed,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你和孩子们是我的温暖 食粮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.04,0:43:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}clothe, pacify, and rejuvenate me\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}衣被 平静与活力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.00,0:43:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}by never leaving my heart.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为你们永远都在我心中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.05,0:44:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Love, Prisoner Number 7551.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爱你的7551号囚犯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.02,0:44:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're not gonna take that hill from the Japs with bullets, bombs or fists.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}子弹 炸药和拳头无法打败日本鬼子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.08,0:44:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.94,0:44:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're gonna take it with blood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让他们血流成河吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.52,0:44:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whoever spills more, loses.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}流血多的一方就输{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.78,0:44:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And we don't lose.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们不会输的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.20,0:44:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do we?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对不对？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.45,0:44:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.91,0:44:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You lose.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你输了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.25,0:44:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's what I thought.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.05,0:44:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know John Wayne?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你认识约翰·韦恩？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I do.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}认识{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.89,0:44:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What's he like?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是怎样的人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.94,0:44:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You'd love each other.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们一定会喜欢彼此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Isn't he beautiful? Okay.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很美吧？来吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.61,0:44:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mom, I got a new one. Huh?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妈 我想到一个新招{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.94,0:45:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Okay, wait.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.49,0:45:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Come on, you're gonna scare the horse.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}过来 你会吓到那匹马{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.95,0:45:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mom, you'd better come quick!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妈 快点过来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.95,0:45:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Edward Robinson, are you now or have you ever been\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪·华罗宾森 你是否现在或曾经？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.22,0:45:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a member of the Communist Party?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.62,0:45:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm not now, sir, nor have I ever been a member of that party.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我现在不是 以前也没加入过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.96,0:45:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I have always been a Liberal Democrat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直是信奉自由主义的民主党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.09,0:45:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But in your home over the years,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但多年来 在你家中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.93,0:45:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}there have been political meetings attended by those\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}曾举行过多次政治集会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.26,0:45:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that we now know to be communists.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}参与者都是共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.80,0:45:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, sir. Yes, that has now been made clear to me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 我现在才搞清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.18,0:45:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There were tremendous activities and fundraisers...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我家举行过无数活动与募款{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.60,0:45:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that went on in my house during the war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就在战时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.32,0:45:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did not know then\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当时我不清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.82,0:45:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all of their true affiliations\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们隶属什么组织{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.15,0:45:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or the work that they were up to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}进行什么工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.87,0:45:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It never entered my mind\Nthat any of these people were communists.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我从没想过他们可能是共产党员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.16,0:45:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I was duped and used. I was lied to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们愚弄 利用 欺骗了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.13,0:45:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But who used you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁利用你？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.71,0:45:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, um...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}呃…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.82,0:46:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}These sinister forces who probably ran these organizations.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许就是这股邪恶势力策动所有组织{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.55,0:46:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, tell us the individuals that you have reference to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请说出你知道的人名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.19,0:46:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Robinson?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}罗宾森先生？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.82,0:46:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, uh, you had Albert Maltz.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有艾伯特·马尔兹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.36,0:46:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I knew Frank Tuttle and that other fellow.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}法兰克·杜托 还有其他人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.87,0:46:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That top fellow who they say is the, uh, commissar out there.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}被他们称为政委的高层人士是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.37,0:46:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Arlen Hird?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦·赫德？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.88,0:46:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, yes, Arlen Hird.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错 亚伦·赫德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.00,0:46:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I didn't know Dmytryk at all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不认识迪麦特雷克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.75,0:46:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm a commissar now.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我现在成了政委{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.55,0:46:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ian McLellan Hunter... and\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}伊恩·麦克连·汉特 以及…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.34,0:46:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dalton Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.06,0:46:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, Mr. Robinson.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 罗宾森先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.85,0:46:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, sir.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢 先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.23,0:47:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Chairman, I have no further questions.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}主席 我没有问题了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.57,0:47:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Snitch like that in here,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在这里 谁敢这样打小报告{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.53,0:47:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you end up fucking dead.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就死定了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.79,0:47:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Eddie ought to go back to work. He did what he had to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪尽了责任 应当回到工作岗位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.21,0:47:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no, he did what he was forced to do.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不行 他是被逼才开口的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.25,0:47:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, the point is, he did it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}重点是他说了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.76,0:47:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Brave men and boys are fighting this battle against communism.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}勇敢的男人与男孩们 正与共产主义作战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.26,0:47:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They are sacrificing in ways we can't even imagine.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们难以想像他们做了何等牺牲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.93,0:47:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you wanna talk about some asshole's movie career?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而你却担心这个混帐的电影事业？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.93,0:47:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'd see Eddie Robinson and everyone like him dead\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我多希望艾迪及其党羽们的死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.65,0:47:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}if it'd bring back one boy from Korea. Just one.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能换取朝鲜战场一个男孩的性命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.32,0:47:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So what are you saying?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪都合作了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.90,0:47:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guys like Eddie cooperate and get nothing?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难道不能得到好处？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.78,0:47:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That isn't right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样不对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Careful, Duke.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}说话小心点 杜克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.11,0:47:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Or what, Hedda?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么意思 赫达？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.41,0:47:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I'm not careful, what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要是我不小心会怎样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.58,0:48:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I had no idea you were such a softie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不晓得原来你这么软趴趴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.75,0:48:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's me all right. All cuddles.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 我就是柔软好抱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.26,0:48:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Proud of ya, Eddie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以你为荣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.01,0:48:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wasn't easy, I know. But you did good.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这事不容易 但你做得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.60,0:48:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thanks, Duke.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢 杜克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.31,0:48:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm gonna call the studios. The offers will pour in.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会致电片厂 片约将蜂拥而至{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.36,0:48:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sure.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.66,0:48:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thanks.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.33,0:48:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One of the greatest peacetime spy dramas\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}美国史上和平时期最大的间谍案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.46,0:48:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}reaches its climax,\Nas Julius and Ethel Rosenberg are sentenced to death\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已迈入高潮 罗森堡夫妇被判处死刑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.14,0:48:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}for revealing atomic secrets to Soviet Russia.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为他们将核弹机密泄漏给苏俄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.39,0:49:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The junior senator from Wisconsin, Joseph McCarthy,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}威斯康辛州的初级参议员 约瑟夫·麦卡锡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.02,0:49:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is ramping up his investigation into alleged communists he believes\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}正加速调查可疑的共党分子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.19,0:49:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}are infiltrating our government, our military, and our schools.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们可能已渗透入政府 军队和学校{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.36,0:49:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}because the enemy has been able to get the traitors and dupes\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}敌人让叛徒和骗子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.40,0:49:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to do his work within our government.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}潜入我们的政府进行工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.70,0:49:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}One communist on the faculty\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在大学教职员中{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.04,0:49:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}of one university is one communist too many.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个共产党员都不能留{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.57,0:49:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A man is either loyal or he's disloyal.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人们必须忠诚 否则就是不忠诚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.17,0:49:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, Billy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢你 比利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.45,0:50:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're here! They're here!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.12,0:50:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're home! Dad!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们到家了 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.79,0:50:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm being attacked by giants! Ah!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}巨人进攻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.50,0:50:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What have you beautiful creatures done with my little ones?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的孩子怎么变得这么漂亮了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.46,0:50:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Dad, we missed you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸爸 我们好想你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.59,0:50:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Christopher. Mitzi. - Hi, Dad.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 克里斯多福 梅兹 - 你好 爸爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.97,0:50:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My goodness.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.93,0:51:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nikola, look at you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮可拉 瞧瞧你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.93,0:51:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She got real tall.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她个子可真高{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.81,0:51:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, is that lipstick?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是口红吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.23,0:51:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dad...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.19,0:51:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, I've missed you so much. All of you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我好想念你们 你们每个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.00,0:51:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, I'm terribly sorry...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真是抱歉…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.50,0:51:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Buddy! Well, how are you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}巴迪 你好吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.46,0:51:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I got nothing to say to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我对你无话可说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.39,0:51:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Looks like prison has given us the plague.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}监狱似乎让我们染上了瘟疫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.48,0:51:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, well, that Buddy Ross, he was always an asshole.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊 巴迪·罗斯一直都这么讨人厌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.06,0:51:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.27,0:51:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's in trouble too.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他日子也不好过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.90,0:51:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Three movies, three flops. - Oh, really?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 三部电影都赔钱 - 真的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.53,0:51:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look at him. He's trying to sell his soul, but he can't find it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他想出卖灵魂 却不知灵魂在哪里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.37,0:52:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just hope he stays afloat long enough to get the shit sued out of him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}希望他能撑到打完官司再破产{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.37,0:52:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, really? By whom?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗 谁告他？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.04,0:52:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}By me and you and all of us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你 我和大家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.28,0:52:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jeez...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.97,0:52:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We use their capitalist system against them...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}用他们的资本主义对付他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.75,0:52:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In civil court. We go after their money.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上民事法庭索赔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.00,0:52:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- For what they did to us! - No. No. No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 以报一箭之仇 - 不 不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.71,0:52:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We make them swear under oath...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要他们举手立誓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.38,0:52:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no, no. Christ!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别说了 老天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.38,0:52:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Haven't you spent enough time in court?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难道你在法庭待的时间还不够吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.05,0:52:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I know I have. Jesus Christ.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可是受够了 老天爷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.26,0:52:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, what else are we supposed to do?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不然我们该怎么做？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.27,0:52:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We do the one thing everyone says we can't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}做一件所有人以为我们做不到的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.07,0:52:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Look, you're a great writer. We make shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是大剧作家 我们拍的都是烂片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.74,0:52:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't see it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不懂要怎么合作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.28,0:52:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. King, I'm a screenwriter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}金先生 我是剧作家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.41,0:52:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I couldn't write shit, I'd starve.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果我写不出烂片 我会挨饿的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.62,0:52:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Trumbo, we can't afford you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃 我们付不起你的片酬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.58,0:52:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, how much did you pay for the script of that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那部片的剧本你们付了多少钱？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.42,0:52:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Bad Men of Tombstone\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《恫村五虎》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.59,0:53:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}$1,200.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}1200元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.59,0:53:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right. I'll write you a movie for $1,200, then.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 我就写一部电影给你 1200元{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.93,0:53:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you don't want your name on it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而且不愿署名？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.77,0:53:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, you don't want my name on it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}才不是 是你们不想放我的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.42,0:53:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You got that right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.02,0:53:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Especially if you're still, you know, up to stuff.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特别是如果你还在从事那些活动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.11,0:53:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还没收手？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.69,0:53:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Perpetually.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这辈子脱不了身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.49,0:53:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.61,0:53:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You got any ideas?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有什么想法？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.95,0:53:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I just got out of prison.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这个… 我刚刚出狱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.02,0:53:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What about crime?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}何不拍部犯罪电影？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.45,0:53:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A story of a gangster, his rise and fall.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一位歹徒的崛起与没落{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.21,0:53:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've seen that a few times.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这种题材我看到过几次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.96,0:53:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because it always makes money.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为容易赚钱啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.88,0:53:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right, when do I get my goods?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好 我何时能收到？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:40.05,0:53:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Three days.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}三天内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.38,0:53:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A 100-page screenplay in three days?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}三天内写完一百页的剧本？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.84,0:53:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you trying to fuck me?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想搞我吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.68,0:53:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}'Cause if you fuck me, I will fuck you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你如果敢搞我 我就搞死你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.97,0:53:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. King, I've heard this speech.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}金先生 这句话我曾经听过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.73,0:53:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It was better in jail.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}牢里的人 肯定更有气势{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.01,0:54:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"No, boss...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 老板{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.85,0:54:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"He..."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.02,0:54:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you kidding me with this? Hymie, get out here!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在开什么玩笑？海米 快过来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.20,0:54:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hymie, pay the man! He's a genius. Beautiful.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}海米 快雇用他 他是天才 写得太好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.40,0:54:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wait a minute, look. We got Killer in the Swamp.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}稍等 你看我们手头的剧本《沼泽杀手》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.87,0:54:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The best character's the swamp. Oh, oh.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}里头最棒的角色是沼泽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.54,0:54:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Women in Prison.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《女子监狱》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.62,0:54:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dames fighting in their underwear.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}女人穿内衣打架{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.25,0:55:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's perfect, except it stinks.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}题材很棒 但写得烂透了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.54,0:55:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What else, Hymie?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有吗 海米？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.71,0:55:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Pirates. Can't afford the ocean.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}海盗电影 但拍海太贵了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.21,0:55:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}确实{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.80,0:55:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Fix them all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}全部改写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.05,0:55:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You want more, we got more. Oh, baby!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还有更多等着你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.22,0:55:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, what do you think of the new neighborhood?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们觉得新家的环境如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.60,0:55:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I like it. - Yeah, this is nice.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我喜欢 - 很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.23,0:55:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, Dad.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错 爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.51,0:55:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's gonna be good being in town.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}住在城里感觉一定很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.41,0:55:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whoa, look at that!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们瞧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.29,0:55:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I brought you some lemonade. - Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 喝点汽水吧 - 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.08,0:55:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hard work. You holding up okay?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}辛苦了 还搬得动吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.62,0:55:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Pretty good. - All right, thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 没问题 - 没问题 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.80,0:55:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We forgot the towels!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们忘记拿毛巾了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.09,0:55:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, shoot! Wait for me. Wait for me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}糟糕 等等我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.46,0:56:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mitzi... Shh!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}梅兹…嘘…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.14,0:56:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, there are many angry and ignorant people in the world.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}世上有许多愤怒却无知的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.15,0:56:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They seem to be breeding in record numbers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们的繁殖速度似乎屡破纪录{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.24,0:56:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, all we can do as a family\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们是一家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.66,0:57:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is stick together and remain vigilant.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}必须彼此陪伴 保持警惕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.55,0:57:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Mouth of Truth.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"真理之口"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.51,0:57:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Legend is that if you're given to lying,\Nand you put your hand in there,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}传说如果说谎的人手伸进去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.18,0:57:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}it'll be bitten off.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就会被咬掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.52,0:57:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, what a horrid idea!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真可怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.06,0:57:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's see you do it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你来试试看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.40,0:57:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Let's see you do it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你先来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.37,0:57:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sure.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.59,0:57:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hello.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开玩笑的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.88,0:57:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You beast!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这个人 怎么这样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.55,0:57:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a huge hit. Great reviews.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《罗马假日》票房大卖 好评连连{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.72,0:58:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I haven't worked in nine months. You?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我九个月没工作了 你呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.60,0:58:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, there aren't quite enough zeros\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难以糊口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.48,0:58:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in a King Brothers' salary to survive,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}金氏兄弟给的酬劳太少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.23,0:58:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but they need scripts like an army needs toilet paper.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但他们对剧本的需求 就像军队对卫生纸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.98,0:58:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Quality minimum, quantity maximum.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不求品质 只求数量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.78,0:58:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You'd think that when the artistic ambitions of a movie are non-existent,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我原以为舍弃对电影的艺术追求{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.16,0:58:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the work would be tossed off in a week.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本能轻易在一周内交出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.91,0:58:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But consistently pleasing two former pinball salesmen\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但要持续取悦二位弹珠台销售员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.67,0:58:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}turns out to be a high hurdle indeed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}结果却是难上青天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.59,0:58:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I've become a stranger in my own house.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我开始成了家里的陌生人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.80,0:58:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Every workweek is seven days. Every day is 18 hours.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一周工作七天 每天18小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.93,0:58:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Every minute, I'm further behind.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}进度却越来越落后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.60,0:58:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They need five of you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们需要五个你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.19,0:58:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Okay, the only question is, can these pinkos write?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}问题是 这些左翼分子会写剧本？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.11,0:58:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, the dapper gentleman in the gray suit\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}短小精悍 穿灰西装的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.98,0:58:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is Ian McLellan Hunter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是伊恩·麦克连·汉特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.28,0:58:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guy who wrote Roman Holiday.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}写《罗马假日》的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.49,0:58:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guy who just got subpoenaed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最近被传唤的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.36,0:58:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Guy who just got nominated for an Academy Award.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}刚被提名奥斯卡奖的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.87,0:59:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Everyone at that table's been nominated.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那桌人都被提名过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.33,0:59:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There's Alvah Bessie, and Adrian Scott. Arlen Hird.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾伯特·贝西 艾卓安·史考特 亚伦·赫德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.96,0:59:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And Ring Lardner, Jr. and Albert Maltz and...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小文拉纳 艾伯特·马尔兹 以及…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.38,0:59:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It'll be like this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.30,0:59:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll find the writer and work with him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我来找写手合作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.64,0:59:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He'll deliver the script to me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对方提供剧本给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.68,0:59:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If it's good, I'll give it to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}够好我就交给你们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.31,0:59:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If it needs work, I'll fix it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不够好我就改写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.81,0:59:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No one gets paid until you're happy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们觉得满意再付钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.06,0:59:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And these writers, they're... They're all...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些剧作家 他们都是…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.32,0:59:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, they're all black...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们都是黑…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.07,0:59:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Blacklisted.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}黑名单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.15,0:59:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus, you're such a chicken-shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 你也太胆小了吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.99,0:59:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, we're at war with the communists.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们正在和共产分子交战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.03,0:59:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- No we're not. - It's a new kind of war.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们并没有 - 这是新型态的战争{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.20,0:59:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah, if it doesn't exist, very new.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错 根本不存在的战争 超新潮的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.50,0:59:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- What about the Rosenbergs? - What about the Rosenbergs?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 那罗森堡夫妇呢？- 他们怎么了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.54,0:59:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They stole the atom bomb.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们偷了核弹的秘密{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.67,0:59:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They didn't steal it off a fucking camera truck.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们只是没有躲过眼线{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.09,0:59:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So look, we bought a gorilla suit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们既然已经雇了打手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.84,1:00:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We gotta use it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就要写出轰动世界的作品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.60,1:00:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.68,1:00:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, you had five jobs.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你原有五份工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.44,1:00:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And now we got them and now you got none?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在被我们拿走了 你怎么办？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.52,1:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, now I'm free to get five more jobs and five more writers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就有时间再去找五份工作和五个写手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.36,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you each get five more jobs and five more writers and so on.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们每个人如法炮制{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.41,1:00:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To keep that going, we'd have to write every script in the business.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样下去 我们就会垄断市场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.20,1:00:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Arlen, what a devious lad.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦 你真狡诈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.54,1:00:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So who wants to write a gorilla movie?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁想写出轰动世界的电影？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.25,1:00:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who doesn't?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁不想？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.04,1:00:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We now work at midnight\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们接下来要在黑夜里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.42,1:00:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in thick fog among strangers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}在浓雾中与陌生人做生意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.55,1:00:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not literally.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这只是一种形容{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.39,1:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're running a family business.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要经营家族事业{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.39,1:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We'll be adding new phone lines,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}接上新的电话线后 接听电话时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and when answering, never say, "Trumbo residence."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}千万别说 这里是特朗勃家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.06,1:00:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll be writing for various producers under different names.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我会用不同笔名和不同的制片人合作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.40,1:00:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whomever they ask for, you come find me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不论谁来电 记得来找我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.90,1:01:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Or take a message.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或留言{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.74,1:01:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hello?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.04,1:01:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is John Abbott there?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}约翰·亚伯特在吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.25,1:01:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, sir, may I take a message?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他不在 方便留言吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.83,1:01:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The door must be answered at all hours.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不论何时都要有人应门{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.13,1:01:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Got a pickup for Sally Stubblefield.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我来收莎莉·史塔波斐的邮件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.47,1:01:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Can I get your mom to sign?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可以请令堂签名吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.64,1:01:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.44,1:01:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dictation, shorthand and typing will be learned.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你们要学习听写 速记和打字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.11,1:01:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Those of legal age will have one of the most important jobs imaginable.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}成年人则负担最重要的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.44,1:01:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Courier.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}秘密快递{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.36,1:01:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Scripts must be delivered to producers without raising suspicion.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}使命必达 且不能让人生疑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.03,1:01:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Any questions? Concerns?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有问题或担忧吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.37,1:01:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Yes, Nikola. - Is there a schedule?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 妮可拉 请说 - 有时间表吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.46,1:01:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.62,1:01:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I need to know when I can do homework.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得安排时间做作业{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.79,1:01:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I'm part of a fundraising committee for Negro voting rights.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}募款支持争取黑人投票权{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.21,1:02:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Plus, every other Friday, we have meetings for Student Council.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每周五 学生会还要开会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.63,1:02:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm... I have to...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我必须…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.05,1:02:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niki, we'll figure something out, sweetheart.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别担心 会有办法的 宝贝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.80,1:02:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Won't we?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.85,1:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And protests continued as the Supreme Court may soon take up\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人们持续抗争 近期最高法院{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.64,1:02:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the issue of racial segregation.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可能得回应种族隔离政策{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.97,1:02:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Negros in Southern towns and cities\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}南方城镇的黑人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.08,1:02:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}have taken to the streets in large numbers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大量走上街头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.15,1:02:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All under close scrutiny by local law enforcement.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当地执法者正加强控制{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.57,1:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There have been unconfirmed reports of disturbances and rioting.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}许多未经证明的消息指出 可能发生暴动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.49,1:02:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But it is not clear if the violence was initiated by protesters...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但不确定发起暴动的是示威者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.37,1:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nikola!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮可拉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.04,1:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or white vigilante groups.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}还是白人义务联防队{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.70,1:02:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Beyond the South, through the nation...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除了南方 整个国家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.37,1:02:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, there you go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 给你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.75,1:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A few mistakes, not many.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只改了几个地方 错得不多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.55,1:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.67,1:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all top-salaried government officials\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}薪资最高的政府官员{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.59,1:02:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}should make a full public statement of their income...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}应该全面公开他们的收入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.34,1:02:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This concludes our program scheduled for today.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今日节目到此结束{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.62,1:03:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which one is Graham Tauper?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁是"葛拉汉·塔波"？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.38,1:03:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nympho Nun.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}写了《色情修女》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.92,1:03:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.17,1:03:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Great job.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}干得好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.09,1:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh, Elwood Carr, Murder at the Circus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}写《马戏团杀手》的艾伍德卡尔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.59,1:03:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It needs work. I knew the clown did it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}需要改进 我猜到小丑是凶手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:31.55,1:03:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's always the clown.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}凶手永远都是小丑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.39,1:03:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you are The Alien and the Farm Girl.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《外星人与农庄女》是你写的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.06,1:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.64,1:03:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you wrote the alien talking about the rights of the worker.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你笔下的外星人谈论劳工权益{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.77,1:03:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The pathology of capitalism.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}资本主义的病灶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.57,1:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The complacency of the bourgeoisie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及布尔乔亚的自满{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.24,1:03:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't even know what it is and I fucking hate it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我根本看不懂 烂透了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.78,1:03:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, the idea was to use the...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的创作理念是…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.62,1:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I paid you to write a script about\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我付钱请你写的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.33,1:03:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a guy with a giant bug head shtupping a girl in a hayloft.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}大头外星人在干草堆上女人的故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:58.96,1:04:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you write shit\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而你写了这些垃圾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.25,1:04:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that's gonna get me subpoenaed, and stinks!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}会害我被传唤且名声扫地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.96,1:04:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Fix it!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}重写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.13,1:04:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, fuck Frank King.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该死的法兰克金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.76,1:04:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I said, until he's happy, I'd rewrite.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我承诺要改写到他开心为止{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.59,1:04:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you're gonna stay up with that all night, for that crap?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要为了这种垃圾开夜车？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.35,1:04:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}For what?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.43,1:04:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To get it to his high literary and political standards?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达到他的文学与政治标准？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.10,1:04:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, it shouldn't be to anyone's political standards.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这东西不该扯上任何政治标准{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.94,1:04:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's The Alien and the Farm Girl, for Christ's sake.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是《外星人与农庄女》 拜托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.78,1:04:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What the hell were you thinking?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你到底在想什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.19,1:04:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I was thinking.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.61,1:04:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's why I'm a writer. To say things that matter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这就是我写作的初衷 写出重要的事物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.11,1:04:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Remember that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你还记得吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.53,1:04:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I was a reporter. I was nominated for a Pulitzer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是曾入围普利兹奖的记者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.79,1:04:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I fought in Spain, and I know Ernest Hemingway.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我在西班牙服役 还认识海明威{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.21,1:04:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I actually... I know him. - Oh, bullshit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我真的认识他 - 胡说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:44.04,1:04:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And he knows me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他也认识我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.29,1:04:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If I walked into a bar in Paris, he...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}假如在巴黎的酒吧遇见他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.80,1:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Maybe not my name, but he'll...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他可能不记得我名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.22,1:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll get a wave.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但至少会招手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.34,1:04:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yeah.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}希望如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.80,1:04:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You... You won the National fucking Book Award.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你得过该死的国家图书奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.39,1:04:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, what are we doing?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但现在我们在做什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.52,1:05:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Okay, so the alien...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}回到正题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.48,1:05:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The alien impregnates the farm girl.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}外星人让农庄女怀孕了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.65,1:05:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Right. - Why?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 没错 - 为什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.82,1:05:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because he wants to inseminate her and propagate a new species\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为他想播种并繁殖新的物种{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.36,1:05:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- on Earth and take over? - No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 然后占领地球？ - 不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.65,1:05:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because she reminds him of the girl he left behind.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为她让他想起家乡的女孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.74,1:05:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But he's got a bug head.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但他头这么大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.87,1:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His girlfriend's probably got a bug head back home.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他家乡的女孩 头一定也很大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.08,1:05:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You don't get hung up on the looks of someone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人不会迷恋外表{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.37,1:05:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's falling in love with her.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他爱上了她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.83,1:05:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Uh, okay.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.33,1:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're over-thinking.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你想太多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.26,1:05:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Are you all right? - Yeah.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你还好吗？ - 还好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.18,1:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You want to do this later?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要不要休息一下？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.01,1:05:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. Go, please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 请继续{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.85,1:05:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.35,1:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, do you ever miss writing something...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难道你不怀念过去的时光？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.52,1:05:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Forget great, just good?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不说是伟大 但至少是好作品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.19,1:05:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, you must have ideas still, right?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你脑中一定有很多好点子 是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.90,1:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've got a few.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有几个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.78,1:05:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There's one that won't go away.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}其中有一个萦绕不去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.78,1:06:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cleo and I are in Mexico at a bullfight years ago.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好几年前 克莉欧和我在墨西哥看斗牛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.58,1:06:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the bull dies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那只牛死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.75,1:06:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And, uh, thousands of people are just cheering.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}成千上万的观众却在欢呼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.09,1:06:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Three weren't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除了三个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.05,1:06:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cleo, me and this young boy down front,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}克莉欧 我 我们前面的一个小男孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.93,1:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}crying.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他哭了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.98,1:06:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Always wondered why.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直好奇他哭的原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.11,1:06:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, (COUGHS) you write it and you'll know.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}等你找到答案后 就会写出来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.61,1:06:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But please promise me, not for Frank fucking King.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}答应我 别交给该死的法兰克金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.66,1:06:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.58,1:06:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To present the writing awards, here is an actor who also reads.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}颁发最佳编剧奖的演员也热爱阅读{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.37,1:06:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Kirk Douglas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎柯克·道格拉斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.87,1:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niki, hurry!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮琪 快点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.92,1:06:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who's doing it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是谁颁奖？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.55,1:06:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm coming, I'm coming!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来了来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.89,1:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The envelope.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}信封{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.43,1:07:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the Oscar goes to\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥斯卡得主是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.73,1:07:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Roman Holiday by Ian McLellan Hunter. (GASPS)\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《罗马假日》编剧 伊恩·麦克连·汉特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.65,1:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes! That's you, Dad, that's you!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}万岁 爸 你得奖了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.98,1:07:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dad, that is fantastic!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸 太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.53,1:07:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is accepted on behalf of Ian McLellan Hunter.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我代表伊恩·麦克连·汉特领奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.70,1:07:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So do we get to be happy now?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们可以过幸福快乐的生活了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.30,1:07:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't want it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.97,1:07:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I don't want it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也不想要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.01,1:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Your name's on it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上面写了你的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:43.64,1:07:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You wrote it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但剧本是你写的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.18,1:07:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They gave it to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们把奖给了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.81,1:07:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And it's done me wonders.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它让我创造了奇迹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.61,1:07:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Here's the gorilla script.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是轰动世界的剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.24,1:07:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Hey, Dad. - Ah?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 爸 - 在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.61,1:07:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Phone for you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有你的电话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.32,1:08:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}For which name?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}找哪个名字？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.03,1:08:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, you. Some guy named Buddy Ross.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}找你 一个叫巴迪·罗斯的人打来的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.20,1:08:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, is the rumor true? You wrote Roman Holiday?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看来传言是真的？《罗马假日》是你写的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.92,1:08:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What can I do for you, Buddy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我能帮上什么忙吗 巴迪？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.59,1:08:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My movies have all bombed. Dug me into a hole.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}电影票房失利 让我坠入万丈深渊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.93,1:08:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I finally got something going.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}终于要拍一部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.85,1:08:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Classy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}超级大片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.05,1:08:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Three big stars. The script...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我找来三位巨星 但剧本…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.23,1:08:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What script? There is no script.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别提了 根本没剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.19,1:08:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I got 11 writers who fucked me and now the actors are gonna pull out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我找了11个作家都写不好 演员即将退出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.73,1:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And if they do, I lose everything.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}若真如此 我将失去一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:39.32,1:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}When do you shoot?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你何时要拍？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.78,1:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ten days.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}十天后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.37,1:08:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is there anything?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有任何参考资料吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.12,1:08:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There'd be no credit, obviously.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然 我无法让你署名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.00,1:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I can't pay you till we start shooting.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}开拍后才能支付酬劳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.63,1:09:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wouldn't blame you if you spit in my face.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要是你唾弃我 我不会怪你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.60,1:09:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But we did good stuff back then.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我们曾经合作过好作品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.43,1:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We really did.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.77,1:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.90,1:09:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I owe the King Brothers a rewrite.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我还要帮金氏兄弟改写一部剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.24,1:09:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I can't do both.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无法两者兼顾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.07,1:09:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Here it is. I need you to take over.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本在这里 我需要你帮忙接手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.91,1:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you can help that great guy, Buddy Ross.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好让你帮助伟大的巴迪·罗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.87,1:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So we can keep tearing down the blacklist.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样我们才能继续消灭那张黑名单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.21,1:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Jesus, here we go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 又来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.42,1:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is going to be a very big movie, and if Buddy gets a good script...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果巴迪拿到好剧本 会是部卖座大片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.13,1:09:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Which you're gonna give him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本是你给他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.21,1:09:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, which I am going to sell him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是卖给他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.92,1:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}For money, 'cause that's why we did all of this, right?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了赚钱 这就是我们写剧本的目的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.55,1:09:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Was for the money.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}就为了钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.68,1:09:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why can you not see this?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你怎么看不清这点？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.05,1:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If we get one big movie, we can get all the big movies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拍出卖座片 我们就能继续接拍大片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.31,1:09:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And then this whole rotten thing could collapse on the sheer irony\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}讽刺地终结这腐败的一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.65,1:09:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that every unemployable writer is employed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所有被封杀的剧作家都活跃得很{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.27,1:09:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jesus Christ, do you have to say everything\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天哪 你一定要讲得这么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.53,1:10:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}like it's going to be chiseled into a rock?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}冠冕堂皇吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.90,1:10:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm not gonna help you help Buddy Ross!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不会帮你协助巴迪·罗斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.28,1:10:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}God's sake!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.82,1:10:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- You are against every... - No, I...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你总是要拒绝我的好点子 - 不 我…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.58,1:10:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}solid idea that comes up. Let's do something!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}让我们有所作为吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.99,1:10:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}These fuckers did things!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那些混蛋做了伤天害理的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.75,1:10:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We should be suing that cockroach into the ground\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们应该把他们告到一败涂地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.08,1:10:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- along with those congressmen... - There's an idea.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 包括那些议员 - 好主意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.21,1:10:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Yes, and the producers! - Very good one.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 还有制作人 - 太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.29,1:10:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Yes, and the studios! - That'll be better.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 还有片厂 - 这样更好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.80,1:10:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- We should sue them! - Oh, yes, brilliant!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我们应该告上法庭 - 很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:21.76,1:10:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Keep losing. Give all of your money away to lawyers!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}继续打败仗 把钱都送给律师{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.26,1:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'd rather lose for the right reasons.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我情愿为正义而败{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.93,1:10:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.09,1:10:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's still losing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}失败就是失败{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:29.47,1:10:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You lose. I lose. We all lose!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你输 我输 大家都输{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.39,1:10:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Don't you see that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你看不出来吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.31,1:10:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the whole goddamn country stays scared and dead.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}国家依然噤若寒蝉 死气沉沉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.52,1:10:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you really think you can go on living like this forever?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你真以为可以这样过一辈子吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.07,1:10:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I'm not gonna have to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是过不完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.74,1:10:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Arlen, we can do this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亚伦 我们办得到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.74,1:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We can beat them. We can win!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们能打败他们 我们能赢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.08,1:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I don't care if I win. - Bullshit!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我不在乎输赢 - 胡说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.04,1:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Everybody wants to win.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}每个人都想赢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.25,1:10:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, you want to win. I want to change things.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 你想赢 我想改变世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.88,1:11:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I want to win so that I can change things. - No you don't!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 只要赢了就能改变世界 - 才怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.67,1:11:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You want to win so that you can get an Oscar with your name on it this time.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你只想赢得一座标着你名字的奥斯卡奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:05.63,1:11:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And so you can get more money that you burn through, writing shit for idiots!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这样就能赚更多钱来 为那些白痴写一堆烂戏{\r}
