Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.75,1:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So I'm fairly certain that even if the whole goddamn country was on fire,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我敢说就算全国都失火{\r}
