Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.55,1:13:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What? It's ridiculous!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎样？太荒谬了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.02,1:14:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now I've lost my place. Christ's sake!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不知道进行到哪里了 天啊{\r}
