Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.99,1:14:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We both do. I can't let you do this, Rocco.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们都将如此 我不能害你变成这样{\r}
