Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.92,1:15:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He has to be right all the time.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他总是对的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.55,1:15:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}How do you stand it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你怎么能受得了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.68,1:15:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, it's challenging sometimes, especially lately.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有时确实难以忍受 尤其是最近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.01,1:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hey, why don't you come downstairs with me?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不如跟我一起去躺楼下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.02,1:15:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wanna show you something.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想给你看一样东西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.82,1:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You see my gloves?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有看见我的手套吗？{\r}
