Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.25,1:15:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. But you can.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 但你可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.23,1:16:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niki, is that the script already?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮可 剧本好了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.44,1:16:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Fantastic.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}太棒了{\r}
