Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.18,1:16:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, hello. Um, I'm looking for Arlen Hird.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 我找亚伦·赫德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.14,1:16:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo, it's Andrew.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生 我是安德鲁{\r}
