Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.11,1:17:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}they're all true.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他说的都是真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.91,1:17:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Is, uh... Is he home?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他在家吗？{\r}
