Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.44,1:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My dad left something for you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸爸留了一样东西给你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.53,1:17:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a record.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是份记录{\r}
