Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.12,1:17:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Andrew, no.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}别这么说 安德鲁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.04,1:17:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I owed him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是我欠他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.34,1:18:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The debts are all mine.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这些都是我欠的债{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.93,1:18:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
