Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.44,1:18:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's everything that we owe you. Arlen included.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们欠你的 包括亚伦在内{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.77,1:19:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, now, that was a gift.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 我不打算要回来{\r}
