Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.54,1:19:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Fine. Fine. But first you're gonna listen.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧 但请听我解释{\r}
