Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.60,1:19:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No offers, not even an audition.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有戏约 连试演都没有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.90,1:19:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}People would see me, cross the street.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}人人都与我保持距离{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.28,1:19:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}People I loved.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那些我爱的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.57,1:19:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}People I made rich.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及靠我发大财的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.28,1:19:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I sat in front of that committee.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我被传唤至委员会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.74,1:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why? I didn't do anything.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是为什么 我可什么也没做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.41,1:19:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}None of us did anything. We were all stupid babies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们什么都没做 只是不懂事的小娃儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.62,1:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}With no business in any of it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没做任何不法勾当{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.79,1:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just wanted my life back.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只想回到原本的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.30,1:20:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They had every name. Yours, Arlen's, everybody's.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们掌握了每一个名字 包括你和亚伦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.14,1:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I didn't give them anything they didn't already have.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我提供的资讯 他们早就有了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.47,1:20:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I ended it, is all. I just... I ended it!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我终结了这一切 仅此而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.44,1:20:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Eddie, you don't end something like this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾迪 提供他们无权过问的资讯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.28,1:20:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}By giving them what they have no right to ask.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没办法终结任何事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.32,1:20:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're gonna tell me how I should have handled it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要教我该怎么做吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.58,1:20:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Like you handled Congress?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}像你对付议会那样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.08,1:20:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you're saying that you're proud of what you did?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}难道你以这件事情为荣吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.12,1:20:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Proud? Who the hell gets to be proud?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁有资格感到荣耀？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.00,1:20:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You. You do.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.50,1:20:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You with your fake names and your fronts.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}使用那些假名和掩护{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.63,1:20:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You've got all the work you want.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}成功重返编剧事业{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.09,1:20:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I gotta go out in the world every day.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而我却必须每天亲身面对世界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.18,1:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is my work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是我的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.06,1:20:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've got nobody else to be.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没办法化身为另一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.85,1:21:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did what I had to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我当时别无选择{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.02,1:21:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You did what you wanted, Eddie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你做得心甘情愿 艾迪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.52,1:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you did it for more.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为了获得更大的成功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.94,1:21:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}More movies, more money,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}接拍更多电影 赚更多钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:11.66,1:21:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}more dead bullshit on your walls.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}买更多死人画的烂东西挂在墙上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.46,1:21:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What I did, I did, but did you ever wonder how many years\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的事我自己承担 但你害亚伦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.25,1:21:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}you hacked off Arlen's life?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}少活了多少年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.05,1:21:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To show the world what a rebel genius you are.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只为了昭告天下 自己是个叛逆天才？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.31,1:21:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You live with that!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你必须承担这个责任{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:53.91,1:21:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Drinking alone?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一个人喝吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.16,1:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Preferably.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我愿意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.54,1:22:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And what are you up to these days?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你最近都在忙什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.29,1:22:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, Hedda, another one of these and I just may tell you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 也许再喝一杯我就会告诉你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.21,1:22:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, then I'm buying.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我请你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.59,1:22:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Usual. Same again.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一样的再来一杯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:12.01,1:22:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, Miss Hopper.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是 霍珀小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.72,1:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, come on, I hear the rumors.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}拜托 我听见谣言了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.06,1:22:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Show me you're still in the game, fighting the good fight.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}告诉我 你仍在战场上英勇奋战{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.64,1:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Come on, rub my face in it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}快来打我的脸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.60,1:22:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Whisper a movie you've written in secret.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}告诉我你在偷偷写哪一部片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.98,1:22:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Maybe I've even heard of it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许我已经听说过了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.78,1:22:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Maybe you have.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.19,1:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sorry, sorry, sorry, sorry... I'm filming. It's crazy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉 拍片忙坏我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.20,1:22:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Buddy, do you know Dalton Trumbo?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}巴迪 你认识达尔顿·特朗勃吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.00,1:22:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, I believe we have worked together before.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}认识 我们以前曾经合作过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.67,1:22:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What was it? Was it MGM?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是在米高梅吗？好几百年前的事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.25,1:22:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A million years ago. Nice to see you again, Buddy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很高兴再次见到你 巴迪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.88,1:22:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I hear your new script's in trouble.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听说你的新剧本难产{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.76,1:22:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Maybe you should hire Dalton.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许你该雇用他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.38,1:22:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He used to be pretty good, and price-wise, he'd be bargain basement.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他以前写得很好但很贵 现在应该会便宜点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.76,1:23:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not that you'd ever do it. Not after Buddy named names.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你以前不愿意 但巴迪把你供出来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.18,1:23:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, you didn't know?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不知道吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.77,1:23:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Word was he had hired someone he shouldn't have.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谣传他雇用了一个不该雇的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.98,1:23:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So he got subpoenaed. He had to testify.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以他被传唤出庭作证{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.07,1:23:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Closed session. No press. Makes it easier.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}过程不公开 没上新闻 这样能容易点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.74,1:23:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So, he named you, of course.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以他当然就把你供出来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.28,1:23:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now he's been cleared. Gets to make his movie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在他已恢复清白 继续拍片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.12,1:23:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}In a way, thanks to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都要感谢你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.96,1:23:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Drink, Buddy? You look as if you need one.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要喝一杯吗？你看起来需要酒精{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.05,1:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Democrats voting for segregation.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你相信吗？民主党竟然赞成种族隔离{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.76,1:23:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, the Southern Dixie-crats.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保守的南方民主党人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.93,1:23:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We started a petition for total integration.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们已开始联名上书消除种族差别待遇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.39,1:23:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There it is.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}联名书在这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.56,1:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I already have over 1,000 signatures.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}已有超过一千人签名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.10,1:23:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I'd be happy to make it 1,001.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那我很乐意当第一千零一个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.94,1:23:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And this is the new draft\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是新的剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.85,1:23:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that needs to be delivered to Hymie King in Agoura.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要送去阿古拉山给海米金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.53,1:23:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Wait, Agoura? I thought the Kings were in Hollywood.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}阿古拉山？我以为金氏兄弟在好莱坞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.03,1:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, no, no, no. These are the rewrites.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 这是改过的剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.78,1:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're to be shot tonight, so Hymie needs them on the set right away.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}今晚就要拍 必须立刻送到拍摄现场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.91,1:24:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Agoura's 40 miles.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}阿古拉山距离60几公里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.54,1:24:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes, I'm sure Chris knows that by now.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 克里斯现在知道了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.70,1:24:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, he can't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他去不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.37,1:24:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'm sorry?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.50,1:24:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He has a date. He's taking her to a movie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他有约会 要带女生去看电影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.21,1:24:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, all right, then, Nikola, you'll deliver the draft.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那么 妮可拉 就由你送去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.26,1:24:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I have a protest.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我要示威{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.34,1:24:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Since when do protests have hard start times?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}示威游行需要准时开始？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.43,1:24:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll take it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我送去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.55,1:24:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Nikola will take it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}妮可拉会送{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.64,1:24:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I said I can't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我说了我不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.56,1:24:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Young lady, you will.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}小姐 你必须送去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.39,1:24:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is important.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这很重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.60,1:24:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So is this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这也很重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.73,1:24:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is important to me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这对我而言很重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.40,1:24:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And the date's important to Chris, so figure something else out.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}约会对他而言很重要 你想别的办法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.33,1:24:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Move on! He needs those now!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}动作快点 人家马上就要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.63,1:25:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, honey...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}亲爱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.01,1:25:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}She hasn't been gone that long, and it's really not that late.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}她离家不算太久 现在也不算太晚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.19,1:25:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You know, this is a blatant attempt to manipulate worry.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}显然她是故意要让我们担心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.45,1:25:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do you know when I realized that I had to leave Hal?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道我何时决定离开哈尔的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.20,1:25:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hal? Hal who?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈尔是谁？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.45,1:25:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My first husband Hal.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我的第一任丈夫{\r}
