Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.34,1:31:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's the story of a young Mexican boy and his pet bull.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}关于一个墨西哥男孩与他养的牛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.55,1:31:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Sounds a little fruity. What's it called?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}听起来不太卖钱 片名叫什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.35,1:31:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Brave One. Oh, one problem though.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《勇敢的人》 但有一个问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.06,1:31:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Expensive?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}成本高吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.39,1:31:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Worse.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}烂问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.56,1:31:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's good.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是个好剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.16,1:31:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who told you? What else did they say?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谁告诉你的？他们还说了什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.42,1:31:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You too. And thank you, Frank.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你也是 谢谢 法兰克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.09,1:32:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.60,1:32:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Brave One has been nominated for an Academy Award.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《勇敢的人》入围了奥斯卡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:11.27,1:32:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Really? - Yes, really!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 真的吗？- 真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:16.78,1:32:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's crazy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}太疯狂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.07,1:32:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I don't know. It's like Roman Holiday.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不就和《罗马假日》当时一样？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.95,1:32:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, Hymie, this is nothing like Roman Holiday.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}海米 和《罗马假日》天差地别{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.95,1:32:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Roman Holiday had a guy with a name and a body\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《罗马假日》的挂名编剧真有其人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.08,1:32:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}they could give the award to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们还可以发奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:29.12,1:32:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There is no Robert Rich. Who gets the thing if it wins?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但劳勃瑞奇是捏造的名字 谁去领奖？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.38,1:32:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, maybe it won't.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许不会得奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.13,1:32:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I mean, it's not that good. No offense.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这部片又没多好 无意冒犯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.80,1:32:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}None taken.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不介意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.30,1:32:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And now I'd like to say two of the most beautiful words\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}欢迎电影界最美丽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.64,1:32:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}in the motion-picture industry, Deborah Kerr.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}黛博拉·蔻儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.98,1:32:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The nominations for Best Motion Picture Story are,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥斯卡最佳编剧入围的有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.40,1:32:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Robert Rich for The Brave One,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}劳勃·瑞奇的《勇敢的人》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.44,1:32:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Leo Katcher for The Eddy Duchin Story,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}李奥·凯驰的《艾迪杜钦传》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.07,1:33:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Jean-Paul Sartre for The Proud and the Beautiful,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}尚·保罗·沙特的《奇异的爱情》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.82,1:33:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and Cesare Zavattini for Umberto D.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及塞沙尔·萨瓦提尼的《风烛泪》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.99,1:33:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The envelope please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请把信封给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.67,1:33:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The Brave One, Robert Rich!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}得奖的是《勇敢的人》劳勃·瑞奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.33,1:33:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dad!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}爸！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.80,1:33:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You won! Who's that guy?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是谁？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.09,1:33:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Jesse Lasky Jr., Vice President of the screenwriter's branch\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}由编剧工会副主席{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.35,1:33:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}of the Writers Guild, will accept the award for Mr. Rich.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杰斯·拉斯基二世 代为领奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.18,1:33:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}On behalf of Robert Rich and his beautiful story,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我代劳勃·瑞奇与他的优美故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.31,1:33:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}thank you very much.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢各位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:31.94,1:33:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So weird.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真诡异{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:36.69,1:33:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We can't find Mr. Rich anywhere. He apparently...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我到处找不到瑞奇先生 显然他…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.11,1:33:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who the hell is Robert Rich?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}劳勃·瑞奇究竟是何方神圣？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.70,1:33:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I gotta go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我得挂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.11,1:33:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It had better not be who they say.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最好不要是谣传的那个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.62,1:33:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Trumbo. Yes?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}特朗勃先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.16,1:33:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you Robert Rich?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你就是劳勃·瑞奇？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.02,1:33:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Did you write The Brave One?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《勇敢的人》是不是你的作品？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.37,1:33:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you see, it's my policy\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一向不作声称{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:55.13,1:33:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}not to claim credit for any one movie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}自己参与过任何电影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.34,1:34:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That way, it's possible that I had something to do with all of them.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不然每部电影岂不是都有我的份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.97,1:34:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Except the stinkers, which were all written\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然烂片除外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.05,1:34:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}by my enemies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那都是我的敌人们写的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:05.72,1:34:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What's your position on the blacklist?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你在黑名单属于哪个位置？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.39,1:34:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, on it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我就在黑名单上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.39,1:34:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Along with thousands of others.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}跟另外数千人列在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.64,1:34:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are you using this Robert Rich controversy to try and end it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是否试图以劳勃·瑞奇的争议终结黑名单？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.40,1:34:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}See, The Brave One is a nice little picture.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《勇敢的人》是部好片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:23.57,1:34:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And if rumors of my involvement\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果谣传我有参与该片能帮助票房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.41,1:34:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}can help sell tickets, well, then, good.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我欣然接受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.66,1:34:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And if the strange circumstances\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果这种作者不明的怪事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.25,1:34:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}of its authorship raised a few questions,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}能激起讨论{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.04,1:34:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}well, even better.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就更好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.54,1:34:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Trumbo? - Yes?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 特朗勃 - 是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.21,1:34:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Phone for you. - Well, who is it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 有人来电找你 - 是谁？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.76,1:34:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Some crazy guy, says he's Kirk Douglas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}自称寇克·道格拉斯的疯子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.22,1:34:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Really? Huh. Well, thank you, Nikola.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}真的？谢谢你 妮可拉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.07,1:35:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Niki? Kirk.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你是妮可？我是寇克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.91,1:35:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kirk.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:12.45,1:35:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dalton.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达顿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.91,1:35:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My apologies.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.04,1:35:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We've had more than our share of crank calls lately.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最近有太多恶作剧电话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.79,1:35:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- I can imagine. - Please have a seat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 我能想像 - 请坐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.59,1:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}May I get you a drink?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想喝什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.75,1:35:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. No thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不必了 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.88,1:35:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}All right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.47,1:35:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- So? - I'm doing a new picture.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 所以？- 我接了一支新片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.93,1:35:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I just got the script.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}刚刚收到剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.72,1:35:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That must be seven hours of entertainment there.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看来是长达七小时的娱乐大片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.23,1:35:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Not a single page is entertaining.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可是没有一页有趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.81,1:35:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But there's a good story in there somewhere.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但里头有个动人故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.15,1:35:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}About one man who tried to take on the whole world.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}关于一个试图对抗全世界的男人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.32,1:35:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, you've got me so far.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这有点意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.95,1:35:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He was a slave who led a revolt against the Roman Empire.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}身为奴隶的他 起义反抗罗马帝国{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.16,1:35:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Now, what's the title?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}片名叫什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.08,1:35:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Spartacus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《斯巴达克斯》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.00,1:36:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no, no.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不不不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.13,1:36:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I can't tell you what I'm working on now, except to say that\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能说自己正在写什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.09,1:36:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}the blacklist is alive and well and so is the black market.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只能说 既然有黑名单 就有黑市{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.76,1:36:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, yes, you can quote me on that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 你可以引用这段话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:12.47,1:36:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Seeing my name in the papers drives certain people out of their minds.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看见我的名字上报 会让一些人抓狂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.10,1:36:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Of course. Here he is.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.81,1:36:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Kirk. - Hedda.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 你好 寇克 - 你好 赫达{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.19,1:36:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'd like you to meet a friend of mine, Bob Stripling.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是我朋友 鲍伯·史崔普林{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.69,1:36:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}House Un-American Activities Committee.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}来自非美活动调查委员会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.53,1:36:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Douglas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}道格拉斯先生 你好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.03,1:36:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. Stripling.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}史崔普林先生 你好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.37,1:36:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Drink?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喝点东西吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.66,1:36:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不了 谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.00,1:36:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You said it was important.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你有要事找我？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:43.50,1:36:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Only if you hired Dalton Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只要你雇用了达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.22,1:36:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Who I hire is my business.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我雇谁是我的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.72,1:36:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, Mr. Douglas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 道格拉斯先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:52.22,1:36:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's ours.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这关我们的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.05,1:36:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:55.18,1:36:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}'Cause we have to keep this country safe.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为我们要维护美国的安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:57.39,1:36:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And how are you doing that?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么维护？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.14,1:37:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, why don't I show you by putting you on the stand?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}要不请你上证人席看看吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.15,1:37:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda, is your friend trying to scare me?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 你朋友打算恐吓我？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.73,1:37:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's just trying to show you the way things are.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他只是想让你知道 该怎么做事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:09.99,1:37:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Maybe I don't like the way things are.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或许我不喜欢这样做事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.32,1:37:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kirk, we've known each other a long time.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克 我们认识多年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.91,1:37:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Since when did you become such a bastard?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你什么时候变成了一个混帐？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:19.58,1:37:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I was always a bastard. You just never noticed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我一直都是个混帐 只是你没发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.77,1:37:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么事？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.86,1:37:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wish to see the man who wrote this.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我想见这部戏的编剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.19,1:37:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please, come in.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请进{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.91,1:37:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.95,1:38:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am Otto Preminger.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是奥图·普莱明杰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.29,1:38:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The director.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是个导演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.92,1:38:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Forgive me, I...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.09,1:38:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've just finished work a few hours ago. I...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我几个小时前才刚忙完{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:10.80,1:38:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A copy of which I've read.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我读完了你的剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.72,1:38:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But how could...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么可能？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.30,1:38:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just had that delivered this morning.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我今天早上才寄出的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.26,1:38:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am Otto Preminger, the director.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我是奥图·普莱明杰 我是导演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.93,1:38:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请进{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.40,1:38:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, yes, my youngest thinks\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我最小的孩子认为{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.65,1:38:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that I can end the suffering of all broken birds.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}养鸟可以纾压{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.83,1:38:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}As can I, with a broiler.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我都是吃烤鸟纾压{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.75,1:38:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Are your duties completed for Mr. Kirk Douglas?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克·道格拉斯委托你的剧本 写完了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.17,1:38:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, but I do have two weeks off for Christmas.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 但我有两周的圣诞假期{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.67,1:38:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}During which time you will work with me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这段期间你要跟我一起工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.30,1:38:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Will I?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:58.18,1:39:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If you're as intelligent as your writing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你跟你的剧本一样聪明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.18,1:39:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And as greedy as your reputation.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并且与你的名声一样贪婪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.02,1:39:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It is an adaptation of the novel Exodus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们要改编小说《出埃及记》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.36,1:39:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You've read it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你读过吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.52,1:39:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.03,1:39:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A colossal bestseller.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是本超级畅销书{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.28,1:39:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Very nearly a perfect piece of shit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}几乎难看得要死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:16.11,1:39:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But there's a good story in there somewhere.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但里头有个好故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:22.04,1:39:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I have no idea.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我没概念{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.00,1:39:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But I have Paul Newman.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但我找来了保罗·纽曼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.33,1:39:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We have spoken. He is a little reticent,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们谈过了 他有点谨慎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.21,1:39:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}but I believe, at the right price, he will accept.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但价钱谈拢 他就会接受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.30,1:39:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So you're doing it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你要接吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.84,1:39:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I think it's the only way to get him to leave.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是唯一能赶走他的方法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.51,1:39:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's very important.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这很要紧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.22,1:39:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Poor Mr. Preminger.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可怜的普莱明杰先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.98,1:39:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He thinks he's the cat and you're the mouse.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他以为他是猫 而你才是老鼠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.91,1:40:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, look at that. Perfect.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}瞧瞧 太棒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.02,1:40:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hey, Mitzi, what's that? A Russian doll?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}梅兹那是什么？俄罗斯娃娃？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.67,1:40:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh! What is this, Santa?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是什么 圣诞老人？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.83,1:40:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just a little something for Mrs. Claus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}献给圣诞婆婆的小心意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:13.88,1:40:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll open it later.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我等等再拆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.17,1:40:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Christmas is over.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}圣诞节结束了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.01,1:40:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.72,1:40:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Did you read the new scenes?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你读了最新写的那几场戏？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.35,1:40:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Dreadful. Keep up this level of work,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}糟透了 继续保持这种水准{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.60,1:40:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and I will see to it your name is on my movie.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的名字就会在我的电影里出现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.44,1:40:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To take the blame.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以承受骂名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.07,1:40:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, there you go.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}好了 拿去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.71,1:40:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ooh! Hello. Hi, Sammy.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你好 山米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:51.29,1:40:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, do you know that Kirk Douglas gave me this bird?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你知道它是寇克·道格拉斯送的吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.13,1:40:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a distraction.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它会害你分心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.26,1:40:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No. No, not at all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}完全不会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.30,1:41:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I named him Sam Jackson.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我给它取名为山姆·杰克森{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.64,1:41:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He wrote Spartacus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《斯巴达克斯》就是他写的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.06,1:41:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:10.14,1:41:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Better. - Thank God.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 有进步 - 感谢老天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.90,1:41:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But it simply lacks genius.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但还不是天才之作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:16.48,1:41:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Otto, if every scene is brilliant,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥图 如果每场戏都很精彩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.65,1:41:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}your movie is going to be utterly monotonous.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你的电影会变得单调乏味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.32,1:41:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll tell you what.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我告诉你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.62,1:41:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You write every scene brilliantly,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你把每一场戏写得精彩无比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.75,1:41:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and I will direct unevenly.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而我会导得高潮迭起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.50,1:41:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What is it, dear?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}什么事 亲爱的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:40.34,1:41:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.84,1:41:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, hello, Kirk.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}哈啰 寇克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.18,1:41:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Merry Christmas. Thank you, Mitzi.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}圣诞快乐 谢谢你 梅兹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.35,1:41:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Otto. How are you?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥图 你好吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:49.14,1:41:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am very well, Kirk.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很好 寇克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:52.14,1:41:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I, uh, didn't mean to interrupt.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我无意打断你们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.36,1:41:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, no. No, not at all. Not at all.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不 没这回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:58.53,1:42:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Otto, would you mind if we had a little chat?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}奥图 请让我们谈谈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:00.99,1:42:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Won't be a second.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一会儿就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.53,1:42:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I sort of feel like I walked in on my wife.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我还以为撞见了自己的老婆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.70,1:42:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Do you love him?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你喜欢他吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.87,1:42:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, it's far more lurid than that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}可怕极了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.04,1:42:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's paying me for my services.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他竟然付费买我的服务{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.00,1:42:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}So am I.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:18.13,1:42:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you'll get them again, January 2nd, as promised.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}按约定 我会在1月2日向你交稿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.63,1:42:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I just need you a few days on some of the new scenes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只需要你拨冗几天 写几场新戏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:24.47,1:42:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Of course, but not until the 2nd.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然 但要等2号以后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:28.22,1:42:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I wouldn't ask, but I've never had a director\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我也不想这样 但我没遇过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.23,1:42:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}who's a bigger pain in my ass than Stanley Kubrick.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}比库伯·力克更令人头痛的导演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:35.23,1:42:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The worst part is, he's right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最糟的是 他是对的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.73,1:42:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I wouldn't refuse, but...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不想拒绝你 但…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:45.41,1:42:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I really... This should remain between us.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这是我们之间的秘密{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:49.70,1:42:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Of course.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当然{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:53.58,1:42:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Preminger has declared that...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}普莱明杰宣称{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.58,1:42:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, what he said was,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.71,1:43:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"You keep up this level of work,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"继续保持这种水准"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.26,1:43:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"and I'll see to it that your name is on my movie."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}"你的名字就会在我的电影里出现"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.76,1:43:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Really? - Oh, yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 真的吗？ - 没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.76,1:43:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Those were his exact words.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一字不假{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:15.77,1:43:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Be in touch.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}保持联系{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:17.35,1:43:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Very well.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.86,1:43:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Merry Christmas!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}圣诞快乐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.19,1:43:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You too.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:25.28,1:43:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I suppose he wants you back.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我猜他想要你回去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.03,1:43:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, no. No, no. He...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.70,1:43:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He just stopped by to talk about a screen credit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他来串门 顺便讨论演职人员名单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.17,1:43:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}On Spartacus?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《斯巴达克斯》的名单？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.34,1:43:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, I really shouldn't have said anything.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我不能透露任何细节{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.30,1:43:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You understand.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你懂的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.34,1:43:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Five minutes! Back in five minutes, everybody!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}休息五分钟 大家五分钟后回来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.43,1:43:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kirk,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.60,1:43:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda Hopper just told me the American Legion is going to boycott us\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达·霍珀说 如果你不解雇特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.48,1:44:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}unless you get rid of Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}退伍军人协会将发动抵制活动{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:00.61,1:44:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ed, he's not done with the script.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾德 本片剧本与他无关{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:02.98,1:44:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}His name will never be on the thing.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}片中没有他的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:04.44,1:44:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What's anybody boycotting?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有什么好抵制的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.99,1:44:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kirk... Just a second. Please. Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克 不好意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:08.57,1:44:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Just give me five seconds, please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请让我们独处一会儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.16,1:44:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Listen. Twenty million Americans are saying loud and clear,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}二千万美国人明确表示{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:14.16,1:44:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}they will never buy a ticket to our movie unless you fire one writer.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你不解雇一位编剧 他们就不买票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.08,1:44:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Here's 50! Pick one.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这里有50人 选一个吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:43.36,1:44:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mind if I stick my nose in?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我可以插句话吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:45.15,1:44:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Please.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.36,1:44:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He knows. He sees Kirk Douglas coming in and out of here.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他知道内幕 他看见寇克·道格拉斯进出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:52.07,1:44:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And Otto Preminger and his Rolls.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及奥图·普莱明杰和他的劳斯莱斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:56.45,1:44:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He's an idiot. But he's not stupid.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他是个白痴 但他并不笨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.04,1:45:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Has he called the FBI?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他向联邦调查局告密了吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:02.25,1:45:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Congress?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}国会呢？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.63,1:45:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}No, because everything they can do, they've already done.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有 因为他们能给你的惩罚早就给了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.17,1:45:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That Oscar belongs to you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那座奥斯卡奖是属于你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.30,1:45:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Get it!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}去拿回来吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.56,1:45:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My God! You're nothing like me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}天啊 你一点都不像我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.98,1:45:22.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You're worse.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你比我更可怕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.11,1:45:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}For the record, you're Robert Rich?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请你正式声明 你是劳勃·瑞奇？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.78,1:45:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:32.86,1:45:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've been through the whole list, Ed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我看过名单了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.41,1:45:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're all hacks.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上面都是假名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.70,1:45:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you wrote The Brave One?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《勇敢的人》是你写的？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:37.70,1:45:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I did.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:40.04,1:45:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ed, let me call you back.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾德 我等等回电给你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:41.12,1:45:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Why come forward now?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}为何你现在站出来？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:43.75,1:45:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, as someone who has been thoroughly investigated\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我被非美活动调查委员会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:46.55,1:45:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}by the House Un-American Activities Committee,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}彻底调查过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.80,1:45:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I started wondering, why hasn't anyone taken\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我实在好奇 为何没人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.14,1:45:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}a good long look at them\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}审查这个组织{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:56.18,1:45:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and their work in the movie industry?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及他们对电影产业造成的影响？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:45:58.68,1:46:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You see, they were convened to uncover enemy agents,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该组织的宗旨是 揪出敌方特工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:04.15,1:46:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}expose communist conspiracies and write anti-sedition laws.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}揭露共产阴谋 并制定反叛乱法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.78,1:46:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Well, here we are, thousands of hours\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但经过了数千小时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:12.99,1:46:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and millions of dollars later.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}耗费了数百万元之后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.82,1:46:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Agents uncovered, zero.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有任何特工被揪出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:19.37,1:46:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Conspiracies exposed, zero. Laws written, zero.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}没有任何阴谋被揭露 没有任何法条被制定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.58,1:46:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You see, all they do is deny people their right to work.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们所做的只是否定别人的工作权{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:30.21,1:46:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And they can't even get that right.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我因此丧失权益{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.59,1:46:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Academy Awards, two.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}以及二座奥斯卡奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:39.14,1:46:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And how does that feel?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你作何感想？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:40.52,1:46:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To have so undermined the blacklist that it's almost a joke.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}深深伤害你的黑名单 竟然只是个笑话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.60,1:46:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A joke?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}笑话？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:49.11,1:46:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I know the blacklist that produced Robert Rich.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这张创造出劳勃·瑞奇的黑名单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.70,1:46:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've seen its horror and cruelty.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我见过它的可怕与残酷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.87,1:47:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}A hideous waste of life\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}它可憎地浪费我过去的人生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:02.08,1:47:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}as I've walked in the long line of its anonymous.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我只能长年做个无名氏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:07.75,1:47:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I cannot invent one more witticism about Robert Rich\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我无法再巧妙捏造出下个劳勃·瑞奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.38,1:47:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}or the Oscar he can't claim.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}或另一座无人能认领的奥斯卡奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.64,1:47:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because that small,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为那座小小的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:24.98,1:47:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}worthless golden statue\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}毫无用处的小金人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:28.94,1:47:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is covered with the blood of my friends.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}上面沾满了我朋友们的鲜血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:38.95,1:47:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I'll get it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我来接{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.45,1:47:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hello? Oh, hello, Otto.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}喂？你好 奥图{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:45.41,1:47:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I've read your last draft.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我读了你最新版的剧本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:47.67,1:47:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What do you think?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你觉得如何？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.96,1:47:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My answer is on the front page of today's New York Times.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}纽约时报今天的头版 就是我的回应{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.43,1:48:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You hated it that much?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}你这么讨厌啊？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.97,1:48:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Merry Christmas, Mr. Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}圣诞快乐 特朗勃先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.61,1:48:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ed, have a seat.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾德 请坐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.59,1:48:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Well, why doesn't he kill him? - Kill him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 为什么不杀了他？- 杀啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.51,1:48:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kill him!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杀了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.80,1:48:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Kill him, you imbecile! - Kill him!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 快杀啊 你这个蠢货 - 杀了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.26,1:48:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kill him!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}杀…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:46.85,1:48:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Great. Great.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}很棒 很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:49.27,1:48:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Marty, have them put up the scene with Varinia and Crassus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}马蒂 播放薇瑞妮亚和克拉苏那一幕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:52.86,1:48:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Listen, Kirk, I... - One second.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 听我说 寇克 - 等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:01.49,1:49:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Warren, I'd like you to put out a press release.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}华伦 我想请你发一则新闻稿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:05.74,1:49:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The screen... One second, Warren.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}该片…等等 华伦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:08.46,1:49:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What do you remember when you think about Spartacus?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}想到斯巴达克斯 你会想起什么？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:15.30,1:49:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He was a man who began all alone like an animal.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他像只动物般孤身起义{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:20.18,1:49:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yet on the day he died, thousands and thousands\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但他死去那天 却有千千万万人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:23.26,1:49:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}would gladly have died in his place.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}愿意替他而死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:26.68,1:49:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What was he? Was he a god?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这算什么？他是神吗？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:30.81,1:49:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He wasn't a god.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他不是神{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:33.61,1:49:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}He was simple man. A slave.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他只是个男人 一个奴隶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:41.24,1:49:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I loved him.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我爱过他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:43.37,1:49:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Warren, the press release will say,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}华伦 新闻稿这么写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:48.37,1:49:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"The screenplay for Spartacus was written by Dalton Trumbo."\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}《斯巴达克斯》由达尔顿·特朗勃编剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:51.83,1:49:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.50,1:49:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Kirk, if you don't get rid of Trumbo, I will.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果你不解雇特朗勃 就由我来动手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:49:57.75,1:50:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And right after I quit, you can reshoot all my scenes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那等我离开后 你可以重拍我的戏份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:01.47,1:50:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}You see, Ed, for better or worse,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}艾德 再怎么样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.55,1:50:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I am Spartacus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我演的可是斯巴达克斯呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:12.85,1:50:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There's a picture coming out. It's called Spartacus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这部电影即将上映 名叫《斯巴达克斯》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:17.02,1:50:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's starring Kirk Douglas,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}主演 寇克·道格拉斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:18.86,1:50:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and it is written by Dalton Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}编剧 达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:23.61,1:50:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}If there is some other writer's name on it,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}如果署名是别的编剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:26.20,1:50:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}don't believe it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}请勿相信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:27.95,1:50:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We're on to them.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}他们已经被我们看穿了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:36.33,1:50:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}- Yes? - Now, listen, Ed.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}- 喂？ - 听好了 艾德{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.50,1:50:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We'll picket every theater that movie is in\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们会到所有放映的影院外抗议{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:41.08,1:50:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}unless you pull the prints tonight.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}除非你今晚撤片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.13,1:50:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And you get that traitor's name off it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并将那个叛徒的名字抹掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:45.30,1:50:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hedda, you can't put me in this position.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}赫达 别这么逼我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.22,1:50:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}That's expensive and pointless.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}既浪费钱又没意义{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:48.47,1:50:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Then you can kiss your movie, your studio and your miserable ass goodbye.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那你和你的电影你的片厂 一起吃屎去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:52.64,1:50:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hollywood turns out in force to hail UI's new film spectacle, Spartacus,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}环球影业斥资一千二百万的《斯巴达克斯》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:50:57.19,1:51:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}on the premier of the $12-million picture, in the film colony.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}首映会上许多好莱坞名人现身力挺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:00.65,1:51:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The protesters also showed up to remind everyone of the political controversy\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现场的抗议人士也向我们提示着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:51:04.90,1:51:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}surrounding the making of this film.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}本片制作期间引发的政治争议{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.13,1:52:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Cleo?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}克莉欧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:05.09,1:52:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What is it? What's wrong?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}怎么了 发生什么事？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:15.48,1:52:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's over, isn't it?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}一切都结束了 是吧？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:21.94,1:52:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes. Yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的 没错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:27.57,1:52:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And we made it.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们撑过来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:33.87,1:52:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Yes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.67,1:52:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}President Kennedy enjoyed a rare evening off\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肯尼迪总统难得在晚上的私人时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.34,1:52:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}attending the new Kirk Douglas film, Spartacus.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}看了寇克·道格拉斯的新片《斯巴达克斯》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:46.34,1:52:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}We are here live, awaiting the president's comments.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}记者正在现场 等候总统发言{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:51.14,1:52:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Mr. President, Mr. President, Mr. President!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}总统先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:53.97,1:52:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It's a very controversial film.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}对这部颇具争议的电影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:55.81,1:52:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}What did you think?\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}您有何感想？{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:52:57.43,1:53:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Oh, I think it's a fine picture,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我认为拍得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:00.27,1:53:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and I think it's going to be a big hit.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}应该会大卖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:02.65,1:53:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The implication of Kennedy's approval of this film are wide ranging.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}肯尼迪暗示认可本片 引发广泛讨论{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:06.78,1:53:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The novel was written by a former communist.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}原著小说由前共产党员撰写{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:10.28,1:53:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The screenplay was adapted by a former communist.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}剧本也由前共产党员改编{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.32,1:53:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And this signifies the blacklist may be over,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}意味着黑名单的时代或许已经结束了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.41,1:53:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}as Kirk Douglas and Otto Preminger\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}寇克·道格拉斯和奥图·普莱明杰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.29,1:53:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}have openly hired and credited blacklisted writers.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}公开宣称并挂名雇用黑名单上的编剧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:23.29,1:53:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This is a clear repudiation of a decade-long fight by anti-communists...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这明确批判了数十年来反共人士对艺术界的反对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.14,1:53:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}This next award is for the member\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}下一位得奖者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:33.85,1:53:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}who has advanced the literature of motion pictures.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}提升了电影的文学境界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:36.64,1:53:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Occasionally, there appears among us a person\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有时候 我们中间有些人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:39.73,1:53:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}whose virtues are so manifest,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}品德优秀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.48,1:53:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}who so subordinates his own ego to the concerns of others,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}牺牲小我 照亮他人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:46.07,1:53:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}who lives in such harmony with all the standards of the community,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}顺应社会一切准则{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:50.40,1:53:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that he is revered and loved by everyone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并受到众人的崇敬与爱戴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:53.49,1:53:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Such a man, Dalton Trumbo is not.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}达尔顿·特朗勃 肯定不是这样的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:53:59.33,1:54:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It gives me great pleasure\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我很荣幸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:00.97,1:54:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to present the Writers Guild of America Laurel Award\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}将美国编剧公会终身成就奖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:03.96,1:54:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to Dalton Trumbo.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}颁给达尔顿·特朗勃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:12.68,1:54:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Congratulations.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}恭喜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.80,1:54:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, thank you very much.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}谢谢 非常感谢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:22.06,1:54:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you, thank you very much, ladies and gentlemen.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}感谢各位女士先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:26.52,1:54:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Often, when I stand before the film community,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}通常我出席电影人聚会时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:33.15,1:54:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}there's an elephant in the room.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}房里都有一只看不见的大象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.03,1:54:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那就是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:37.62,1:54:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And I thought I would address that.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}所以我想发表以下谈话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.00,1:54:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}The blacklist was a time of evil.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}黑名单是邪恶时代的产物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:50.42,1:54:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And no one who survived it\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}存活下来的人们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:54.30,1:54:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}came through untouched by evil.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无一不曾被邪恶染指{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:54:59.68,1:55:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Caught in a situation that had passed\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}当时的情况{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:03.06,1:55:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}beyond the control of mere individuals.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}非个人能够掌控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:07.40,1:55:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Each person reacted as his nature,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而我们的行为反映了自己的天性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.94,1:55:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}his needs, his convictions,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}需求及信念{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:13.90,1:55:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and his particular circumstances compelled him to.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}眼前形势强迫我们做了某些事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.20,1:55:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It was a time of fear.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}那是个恐惧的年代{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.16,1:55:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And no one was exempt.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}无人可以幸免{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:25.58,1:55:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Scores of people lost their homes.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}许多人丧失了家园{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:31.88,1:55:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Their families disintegrated. They lost!\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}家庭分崩离析{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.43,1:55:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And in some...\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}有些人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:46.69,1:55:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Some even lost their lives.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}甚至葬送了生命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.65,1:55:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}But when you look back upon that dark time,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但当我们回顾那段黑暗时期{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.37,1:56:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}as I think you should every now and then,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我相信我们偶尔都会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:03.33,1:56:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}it will do you no good\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}指认某人是英雄或恶人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:05.08,1:56:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to search for heroes or villains.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这于事无补{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.79,1:56:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There weren't any.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们之中没有善与恶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:13.63,1:56:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}There were only victims.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}只有受害者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.97,1:56:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Victims, because each of us\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因为我们每一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.43,1:56:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}felt compelled to say or do things\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}都是被强迫做出当时的言行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:24.77,1:56:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}that we otherwise would not.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}否则我们不会那么做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:27.98,1:56:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To deliver or receive wounds\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我们伤害对方 或受到伤害{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:31.98,1:56:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}which we truly did not wish to exchange.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}但其实我们 并不想交换那些伤口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:38.36,1:56:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}I look out to my family sitting there,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}现在看着台下的家人们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:42.03,1:56:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}and I realize what I've put them through.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}我才明白 当时害他们受了多大的苦难{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:48.83,1:56:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And it's unfair.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这对他们太不公平了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:56:54.80,1:57:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}My wife, who somehow kept it all together,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}然而我太太却成功地 维系了家庭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:02.26,1:57:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}amazes me.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}这令我惊奇不已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.77,1:57:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And so what I say here tonight\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}因此 我今晚说的这番话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:10.52,1:57:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}is not intended\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}并不想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:13.15,1:57:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}to be hurtful to anyone.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}伤害任何人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:20.15,1:57:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}It is intended to heal the hurt.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}而是试图治愈伤痛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:26.54,1:57:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}To repair the wounds which, for years,\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}修补多年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:33.38,1:57:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}have been inflicted upon each other.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}不断被撕裂的伤口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:57:38.97,1:57:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}And most egregiously, upon ourselves.\N{\fnSTKaiti\fs16\1c&HE0E0E0&}最糟糕的是 这些伤口已刻在我们身上{\r}
